UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Summary</strong></p><p dir="ltr"></p><ul><li><strong>Make it an ongoing effort.</strong> As your company grows and evolves, so will your customers and market. Conduct customer research regularly to identify shifting buyer preferences and industry trends.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li>Continue to monitor your target market and track changes through ongoing research, such as customer surveys and sales data. Update your target market and marketing strategy as needed.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Avoid stereotypes and assumptions and stick to data.</strong> This is no time for guesswork or wild embellishing. Your persona’s passion for gardening is relevant if you’re selling a revolutionary weeding tool—not gourmet hot dogs.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Monitor your competition on an ongoing basis.</strong> Markets and competitive landscapes continually change. Keep an eye on your top three to five competitors over time by monitoring their social media accounts, website, and other marketing channels.</li></ul><p><ul><li><strong>Put yourself in the segment’s shoes.</strong> Try creating a persona, or imagined character to represent that segment. This helps you humanize the segment and better conceptualize how to treat them.</li></ul></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'module-5-customer-and-marketing-research-module-summary';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"></p><p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p><p dir="ltr"></p><ul><li><strong>Understand&nbsp;</strong></li><li>Have the&nbsp;<strong>capability</strong>&nbsp;to write effective marketing emails</li><li><strong>Know-how&nbsp;</strong>to avoid spam filters when sending emails</li><li>have the <strong>capability</strong>&nbsp;write compelling email subject lines</li><li><strong>Implement</strong>&nbsp;audience segmentation</li><li><strong>Design </strong>an effective email marketing campaign</li><li><strong>know-how </strong>to craft high-performance marketing emails with A/B testing</li><li><strong>Implement </strong>email automation and understand the benefits</li><li><strong>Capable </strong>of measuring the effectiveness of email marketing</li></ul><br><br><p></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'module-9-email-marketing-learning-outcome';
