>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">Once you receive your Customer Service Excellence<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';"> </span></strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Vow Support</span></strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Customer Service Excellence Mentor</span></strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Vow Rewards Tokens</span></strong> (VRT).</span></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3978/mod_resource/content/1/Customer%20Service%20Skills%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer Service Skills Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Improve </strong>your customer service skills</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to work with different customer personality types</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to overcome empathy fatigue in customer service</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to troubleshoot customer issues</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3987/mod_resource/content/1/Customer%20Service%20Skills%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer Service Skills Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'customer-service-excellence-module-2-customer-service-skills';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white;"><strong><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">Welcome to Customer Service Skills Module</span></strong></h4>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">After completing this module you will receive a <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Completion Badge</span></strong> for social media sharing and <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Vow Rewards Tokens</span></strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">This module is <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">one of seven modules</span></strong> from the Customer Service Excellence<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';"> </span></strong>course and after completing all seven modules, you will receive a <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Certificate of Completion</span></strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">Once you receive your Customer Service Excellence<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';"> </span></strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Vow Support</span></strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Customer Service Excellence Mentor</span></strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Vow Rewards Tokens</span></strong> (VRT).</span></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3979/mod_resource/content/1/Customer%20Communication%20Basics%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer Communication Basics Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to communicate effectively with customers</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to personalize customer interactions to build rapport</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to have active listening in customer service</li>\r\n<li><strong>Respond </strong>to customer feedback </li>\r\n<li><strong>Express</strong> empathy in customer service</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-when </strong>to end customer service conversations</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3989/mod_resource/content/1/Customer%20Communication%20Basics%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer Communication Basics Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'customer-service-excellence-module-3-customer-communication-basics';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white;"><strong><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">Welcome to Customer Communication Channels Module</span></strong></h4>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">After completing this module you will receive a <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Completion Badge</span></strong> for social media sharing and <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Vow Rewards Tokens</span></strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">This module is <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">one of seven modules</span></strong> from the Customer Service Excellence<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';"> </span></strong>course and after completing all seven modules, you will receive a <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Certificate of Completion</span></strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0cm; background: white; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #555555;">Once you receive your Customer Service Excellence<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';"> </span></strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Vow Support</span></strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Customer Service Excellence Mentor</span></strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: \'Open Sans\',\'sans-serif\';">Vow Rewards Tokens</span></strong> (VRT).</span></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3981/mod_resource/content/2/Customer%20Communication%20Channels%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer Communication Channels Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>types of customer service channels</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to write outstanding customer emails</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to talk to customers on live chat</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to support customers on social media</li>\r\n<li><strong>Master </strong>customer service phone calls</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>channel switching in customer service</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3991/mod_resource/content/1/Customer%20Communication%20Channels%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer Communication Channels Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'customer-service-excellence-module-4-customer-communication-channels';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Team Management Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of seven modules</strong> from the Customer Service Excellence<strong> </strong>course and after completing all seven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Customer Service Excellence<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Customer Service Excellence </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"></p>\r\n<p><br><br></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3980/mod_resource/content/1/Team%20Management%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Team Management Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>how to manage a customer contact center of your team</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to create a customer service strategy that works</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know how </strong>to empower your team to deliver great customer service.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to measure customer service performance</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> processes for customer support tickets</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3993/mod_resource/content/1/Team%20Management%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Team Management Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'customer-service-excellence-module-5-team-management';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Culture Sensitivity Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of seven modules</strong> from the Customer Service Excellence<strong> </strong>course and after completing all seven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Customer Service Excellence<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Customer Service Excellence </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"></p>\r\n<p><br><br></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3982/mod_resource/content/2/Cultural%20Sensitivity%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cultural Sensitivity Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>why cultural sensitivity matters in customer service</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to deliver exceptional customer service across cultures</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to communicate with cross-cultural customers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to confront cultural bias in customer service</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3995/mod_resource/content/1/Cultural%20Sensitivity%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cultural Sensitivity Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'customer-service-excellence-module-6-culture-sensitivity';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Difficult Situations Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of seven modules</strong> from the Customer Service Excellence<strong> </strong>course and after completing all seven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Customer Service Excellence<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Customer Service Excellence </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"></p>\r\n<p><br><br></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3983/mod_resource/content/1/Difficult%20Situation%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Difficult Situation Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>why customer get upset</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to respond to an upset or abusive customer</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to give an effective customer apology</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to handle refund or cancellation requests</li>\r\n<li><strong>Retain </strong>customers during times of crisis</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to say no to customers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Master </strong>strategies for gaining control of customer conversations</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3997/mod_resource/content/1/Difficult%20Situation%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Difficult Situation Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'customer-service-excellence-module-7-difficult-situations';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Effective Communication Skills Course</strong> has equipped you with the essential techniques and practical tools needed to communicate confidently and professionally in any situation. You explored foundational communication skills, empathy, verbal and written communication, meeting facilitation, presentations, negotiation, persuasion, and strategies for handling difficult conversations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you complete the final exam, take time to reflect on how your communication style has evolved throughout the course and how these new skills can enhance your workplace relationships and career success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to communicate with clarity, purpose, and professionalism—qualities that will strengthen your influence, leadership, and effectiveness in any environment.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'customer-service-excellence-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Project Management Basics Course</strong>, a practical and comprehensive introduction to the essential principles, tools, and strategies used to successfully plan, execute, and manage projects in any industry. Whether you are new to project management or seeking to strengthen your ability to lead tasks, teams, and deliverables, this course provides a clear foundation for understanding how projects are structured and completed.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Throughout this course, you will explore the full project lifecycle—from initiation and planning to execution, monitoring, and closure. You will learn key skills such as communication, scheduling, reporting, scope definition, and change management. Each module breaks down complex concepts into practical, easy-to-apply learning that helps you manage real workplace responsibilities with confidence.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will understand the core practices that ensure project success and be prepared to support or lead projects in your professional environment.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of the <strong>Project Management Basics Course</strong> is to build strong foundational competencies in project planning, coordination, communication, and control. This course aims to help learners understand how structured project management approaches improve quality, efficiency, and team collaboration across any type of task or initiative.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By combining fundamental project management concepts with real-world techniques, this course prepares learners to contribute meaningfully to projects, make informed decisions, and manage project responsibilities with clarity and professionalism.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Upon completing this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand project management fundamentals: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain what projects are, how project management works, and why structured processes improve success rates.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Apply common project frameworks: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify and use project frameworks such as Waterfall, Agile, and hybrid approaches to support project planning and execution.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Communicate effectively within project environments: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use clear communication practices to collaborate with teams, stakeholders, and clients throughout the project lifecycle.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Create and manage project schedules: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Develop realistic timelines, milestones, and task plans using scheduling tools to ensure work is completed on time.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Manage project scope clearly and effectively: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Define project deliverables, boundaries, and requirements to prevent scope creep and ensure alignment with goals.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">6. Prepare project reports and documentation: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Generate progress reports, updates, and documentation that help stakeholders understand project performance.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">7. Implement continuous project improvement: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify opportunities to optimize processes, solve problems, and increase efficiency within the project workflow.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">8. Manage project change confidently: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand how to evaluate, approve, and implement changes while maintaining project control and stakeholder alignment.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Project Management Fundamentals Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Project Management Basics </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4077/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Management%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Management Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>fundamentals of project management</li>\r\n<li><strong>Execute </strong>each of the four phases of project management effectively</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to write a business case for the project</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to create a project plan</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>strategies to increase team effectiveness</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to close a project</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4086/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Management%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Management Fundamentals Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-module-1-project-management-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Project Frameworks Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Project Management Basics </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4078/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Management%20Framework%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Management Framework Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>project management framework</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to choose correct framework foreach project</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>critical path and critical chain project management</li>\r\n<li><strong>Differentiate </strong>between Kanban and Scrum</li>\r\n<li><strong>Choose </strong>the right project management framework</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4089/mod_resource/content/1/Framework%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Framework Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-module-2-project-frameworks';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Project Communications Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Project Management Basics </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4081/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Communication.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Communication.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-why </strong>communication is important in project management</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to communicate successfully during in projects</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to choose communication methods and tools</li>\r\n<li><strong>Put </strong>together a communication plan</li>\r\n<li><strong>Organize and lead </strong>effectively in project meetings</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4091/mod_resource/content/1/Communication%20in%20Project%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Communication in Project Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-module-3-project-communication';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Project Scheduling Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Project Management Basics </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4079/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Scheduling%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Scheduling Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>project scheduling</li>\r\n<li><strong>Define</strong> deliverables and activities</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to estimate time accurately  </li>\r\n<li><strong>Differentiate </strong>task dependencies</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability </strong>to create a resource plan</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>project scheduling techniques </li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4093/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Scheduling%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Scheduling Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-module-4-project-scheduling';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Project Scope Management Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Project Management Basics </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4080/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Scope%20Management%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Scope Management Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>scope management</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>project requirements are and how to collect them</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to define and document scope</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to create a Work Breakdown Structure (WBS)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Address </strong>scope creep</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> best practices for effective scope management</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4095/mod_resource/content/1/Scope%20Management%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Scope Management Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-module-5-project-scope-management';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Project Reporting Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Project Management Basics </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4082/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Reporting%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Reporting Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand</strong> project reporting</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to write a project status report</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability </strong>to control costs through budgeting, tracking and reporting</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to manage and report risk</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use quality management techniques</li>\r\n<li><strong>Apply </strong>best practices for choosing key performance indicators</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4097/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Reporting%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Reporting Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-module-6-project-reporting';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Project Improvement Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Project Management Basics </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4083/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Improvement%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Improvement Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>mistakes to avoid in project management</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how</strong> seek client feedback</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to conduct a post-implementation review</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>a continuous project management improvement</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4099/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Improvement%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Improvement Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-module-7-project-improvement';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Project Change Management Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Project Management Basics<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Project Management Basics </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4084/mod_resource/content/1/Project%20Change%20Management%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Change Management Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>what is Change Management</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to analyze the change impact</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to get sponsorship and buy-in for change</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to implement project changes</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4101/mod_resource/content/1/Change%20Management%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Change Management Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-module-8-project-change-management';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Project Management Basics Course</strong> has equipped you with the essential knowledge, frameworks, and tools needed to participate effectively in project environments. You learned how to plan projects using clear frameworks, communicate with project teams, build schedules, manage scope, report progress, improve workflows, and navigate change confidently.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final exam, reflect on how these skills apply to real workplace projects and how structured project management improves outcomes across any role or industry. Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to support or lead project tasks with professionalism, organization, and strategic thinking.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">You now have a strong foundation to continue your project management journey—whether you pursue more advanced learning, certification, or leadership opportunities.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'project-management-basics-course-summary';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Cybersecurity Basics Course</strong>, an essential program designed to help you stay safe, secure, and confident in the digital world. As our personal and professional lives become increasingly connected, the risks of online threats, data breaches, scams, and cyberattacks continue to grow. This course introduces the core principles of cybersecurity and equips you with the knowledge needed to protect yourself, your devices, and your information.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Through practical guidance, real-world examples, and easy-to-understand concepts, you will learn how cyber threats work, how to secure your data, and how to recognize common manipulation tactics used by cybercriminals. Whether you are a student, employee, business owner, or technology user, this course empowers you to build strong digital safety habits.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to educate learners about the importance of cybersecurity and provide the foundational skills required to stay safe online. The course aims to help individuals identify risks, recognize cyber threats, strengthen personal and workplace security practices, and prevent data loss or compromise.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course prepares learners to confidently navigate digital platforms, protect sensitive information, and contribute to a safer online environment.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand online security fundamentals: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain the basic concepts of cybersecurity, types of threats, and why cyber safety matters for individuals and organizations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Protect your personal and professional data: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use practical strategies such as strong passwords, secure networks, device protection, and safe browsing habits to reduce cyber risks.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Recognize and prevent social engineering attacks: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify common tactics such as phishing, impersonation, scams, and psychological manipulation used by attackers to trick users.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Respond safely to suspicious online activity: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Take appropriate steps when encountering suspicious emails, links, messages, or login attempts.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Strengthen overall digital hygiene: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Practice security habits that keep your accounts, devices, and online presence protected.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'cybersecurity-basics-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Online Security Fundamentals Module from the Cybersecurity Basics Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Cybersecurity Basics</strong> Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Cybersecurity Basics </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Cybersecurity Basics </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4448/mod_resource/content/1/Online%20Security%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Online Security Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:<br></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>cybersecurity</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>best practices for secure internet browsing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> best practices for public WI-FI security</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use social media safely</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to deal with security incident</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4452/mod_resource/content/1/Online%20Security%20Fund%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Online Security Fund Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'cybersecurity-basics-module-1-online-security-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to How to Protect your Data Module from the Cybersecurity Basics Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Cybersecurity Basics</strong> Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Cybersecurity Basics </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Cybersecurity Basics </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4449/mod_resource/content/1/How%20to%20Protect%20your%20Data%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">How to Protect your Data Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:<br></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the importance of confidentiality in the workplace</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability </strong>to create and manage strong passwords</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>multifactor authentication</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use physical security to keep facilities and assets safe</li>\r\n<li><strong>Protect </strong>portable devices and removable media data</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4454/mod_resource/content/1/How%20to%20Protect%20your%20Data%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">How to Protect your Data Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'cybersecurity-basics-module-2-how-to-protect-your-data';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Social Engineering Module from the Cybersecurity Basics Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Cybersecurity Basics</strong> Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Cybersecurity Basics </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Cybersecurity Basics </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4450/mod_resource/content/1/Social%20Engineering%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Social Engineering Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:<br></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>social engineering</li>\r\n<li><strong>Avoid </strong>phishing by implementing best practices to internet surfing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Prevent </strong>phone scams and phishing attacks</li>\r\n<li><strong>Protect </strong>your data against malware</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4456/mod_resource/content/1/Social%20Engineering%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Social Engineering Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'cybersecurity-basics-module-3-social-engineering';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Cybersecurity Basics Course</strong> has equipped you with essential knowledge and practical skills to protect yourself and others in the digital world. You learned how cybersecurity threats work, how to secure your data, and how to recognize dangerous tactics such as phishing and social engineering. These skills help reduce risks, prevent cyber incidents, and support safer online behavior at home, school, and work.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on the importance of digital safety and the preventive measures you have learned. Cybersecurity is an ongoing responsibility, and your awareness plays a vital role in protecting information and maintaining secure digital environments.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to stay cyber-aware, avoid common threats, and practice safer online habits.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'cybersecurity-basics-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Effective Communication Skills Course</strong>, a practical and transformative learning experience designed to help you communicate with clarity, confidence, and impact in both personal and professional settings. Strong communication is one of the most essential skills in today’s workplace—affecting teamwork, leadership, customer relationships, innovation, and overall career success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">In this course, you will explore the foundations of communication, develop deeper empathy and emotional awareness, strengthen your verbal and written communication, learn how to run effective meetings, deliver compelling presentations, and master negotiation and persuasion. You will also practice how to navigate difficult conversations with professionalism and confidence.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be empowered with the tools and strategies needed to express yourself clearly, listen actively, and build strong professional relationships in any environment.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of the <strong>Effective Communication Skills Course</strong> is to equip learners with the essential communication techniques needed to succeed in modern workplaces. This course aims to help individuals understand not only what communication is—but how to use it effectively to build trust, influence others, resolve conflicts, and lead conversations with empathy and clarity.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By combining communication theory with practical, real-world activities, this course helps learners strengthen their ability to express ideas, collaborate with others, and adapt their communication style to different audiences and situations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand core communication principles: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain how communication works and why effective communication is essential in professional environments.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Demonstrate empathy in communication: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use empathy, emotional intelligence, and active listening to build stronger and more respectful interactions.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Apply strong verbal communication skills: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Speak clearly, confidently, and professionally in conversations, meetings, and collaborative settings.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Run effective and structured meetings: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Prepare agendas, lead discussions, and ensure productive outcomes in workplace meetings.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Deliver engaging presentations: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Plan, design, and deliver presentations that communicate ideas clearly and capture audience attention.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">6. Use negotiation and persuasion strategies: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply techniques to influence others ethically, reach agreements, and achieve positive outcomes.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">7. Write professionally and concisely: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Create clear, well-structured, and audience-appropriate written communication for emails, reports, and messages.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">8. Communicate effectively in difficult situations: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use calm, respectful, and solution-focused strategies to manage conflict and challenging conversations.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Communication Fundamentals Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Effective Communication Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4168/mod_resource/content/1/Communication%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Communication Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>is<strong> </strong>communication and why it fails sometimes</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-why </strong>communication skills matter to your professional success</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use verbal, nonverbal and written communication</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to remove common communication barriers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Choose </strong>the right communication medium</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4177/mod_resource/content/1/Communication%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Communication Fundamentals Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-module-1-communication-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Empathy Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Effective Communication Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4169/mod_resource/content/1/Empathy%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Empathy Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>empathy and its importance at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Communicate </strong>with empathy</li>\r\n<li><strong>Overcome </strong>empathy roadblocks</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>strategies for building empathy</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4179/mod_resource/content/1/Empathy%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Empathy Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-module-2-empathy';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Verbal Communication Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Effective Communication Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4170/mod_resource/content/1/Verbal%20Communication%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Verbal Communication Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Improve </strong>your verbal communication skills</li>\r\n<li><strong>Start </strong>a conversation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>strategies for effective listening</li>\r\n<li><strong>Ask </strong>closed vs. open questions</li>\r\n<li><strong>Rectify and Clarify </strong>communication mistakes</li>\r\n<li><strong>End </strong>a conversation positively</li>\r\n<li><strong>Become </strong>an expert verbal communicator</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4181/mod_resource/content/1/Verbal%20Communication%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Verbal Communication Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-module-3-verbal-communication';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Meetings Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Effective Communication Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4171/mod_resource/content/1/Meetings%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meetings Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Conduct </strong>an effective meeting</li>\r\n<li><strong>Set </strong>a meeting agenda</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>group facilitation techniques</li>\r\n<li><strong>Build</strong> consensus in meetings</li>\r\n<li><strong>Manage </strong>conflict in meetings</li>\r\n<li><strong>Speak </strong>up in meetings</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4183/mod_resource/content/1/Meetings%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meetings Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-module-4-meetings';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Presentations Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Effective Communication Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4172/mod_resource/content/1/Presentation%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Presentation Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Define</strong> your presentation objective</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to structure your presentation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Work</strong> with visual aids</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>your visual aid design</li>\r\n<li><strong>Present </strong>your data for the audience</li>\r\n<li><strong>Practice </strong>your presentation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Cope </strong>with presentation nerves</li>\r\n<li><strong>Deal </strong>with questions accordingly</li>\r\n<li><strong>Improve </strong>your presentation skills</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4185/mod_resource/content/1/Presentation%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Presentation Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-module-5-presentations';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Negotiation and Persuasion Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Effective Communication Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4173/mod_resource/content/1/Negotiation%20and%20Persuasion%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Negotiation and Persuasion Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the difference between negotiating and persuading</li>\r\n<li><strong>Distinguish </strong>types of negotiations and use one that is appropriate </li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use negotiation tactics</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use persuasion tactics</li>\r\n<li><strong>Improve </strong>your negotiation and persuasion skills</li>\r\n</ul></div>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-module-6-negotiation-and-persuasion';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Writing Well Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Effective Communication Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4174/mod_resource/content/1/Writing%20Well%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Writing Well Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to write with purpose</li>\r\n<li><strong>Select </strong>the right medium for written communication</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to write for your audience</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to structure your writing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Improve </strong>your grammar, spelling and punctuation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Edit and proofread </strong>your work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Improve </strong>your business writing skills</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4188/mod_resource/content/1/Writing%20Well%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Writing Well Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-module-7-writing-well';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Communicating in Difficult Situations Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eight modules</strong> from the Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eight modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Effective Communication Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Effective Communication Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4175/mod_resource/content/1/Communicating%20in%20Difficult%20Situation%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Communicating in Difficult Situation Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>common workplace issues and how to handle them</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to work with different communication styles</li>\r\n<li><strong>Create strategies </strong>for dealing with difficult coworkers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Create strategies</strong> for dealing with difficult boss</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-when</strong> and how to escalate issues to your boss</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-when </strong>and how to involve HR</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-when </strong>to overcome fear of confrontation and conflict</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to have difficult conversation</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4190/mod_resource/content/1/Communicating%20in%20Difficult%20Situation%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Communicating in Difficult Situation Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-module-8-communicating-in-difficult-situations';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Effective Communication Skills Course</strong> has equipped you with the essential techniques and practical tools needed to communicate confidently and professionally in any situation. You explored foundational communication skills, empathy, verbal and written communication, meeting facilitation, presentations, negotiation, persuasion, and strategies for handling difficult conversations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you complete the final exam, take time to reflect on how your communication style has evolved throughout the course and how these new skills can enhance your workplace relationships and career success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to communicate with clarity, purpose, and professionalism—qualities that will strengthen your influence, leadership, and effectiveness in any environment.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'effective-communication-skills-course-summary';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Building Resilience in the Workplace Course</strong>, a transformative learning experience designed to help you strengthen your ability to adapt, recover, and grow in the face of challenges. In today’s fast-paced, constantly changing work environment, resilience is no longer optional — it is a core professional skill that empowers you to stay focused, maintain well-being, and thrive under pressure. This course will guide you through the foundations of resilience, show you how to reinforce your emotional and physical strength, and help you build career resilience that supports long-term success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Through engaging lessons, relatable examples, and practical strategies, you will learn how to respond to setbacks with confidence, support others through change, and lead with stability and optimism. Whether you are a student, employee, supervisor, or business owner, developing workplace resilience will empower you to perform at your best — even during difficult times.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to equip learners with the tools, habits, and mindsets needed to remain strong and effective in challenging work environments. Resilience enables individuals and teams to bounce back from setbacks, manage stress, navigate uncertainty, and maintain productivity and well-being. This course provides clear, actionable methods to help you cultivate personal resilience and support others as they face difficult situations or organizational change.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of the program, you will be mentally, emotionally, and professionally better prepared to handle adversity and continue progressing confidently in your career.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the fundamentals of resilience: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Define resilience, identify its key components, and explain why it is essential for personal and professional success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Build career-focused resilience skills: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Develop the ability to adapt to change, navigate career transitions, handle workplace pressure, and remain productive under stress.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Strengthen emotional and physical resilience: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply techniques that support mental well-being, emotional stability, physical health, and sustained energy during demanding periods.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Demonstrate resilience in leadership and teamwork: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support colleagues, lead through uncertainty, and model calm and confident behavior during workplace challenges.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Apply practical strategies to thrive through challenges: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use tools such as reframing, stress-management practices, solution-focused thinking, and proactive planning to overcome setbacks.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'building-resilience-in-the-workplace-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Resilience Fundamentals Module from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of five modules</strong> from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course and after completing all five modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Building Resilience in the Workplace Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Building Resilience in the Workplace </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4399/mod_resource/content/1/Resilience%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resilience Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>employee resilience</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to build a resilient team </li>\r\n<li><strong>Build </strong>five pillars of personal resilience</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4405/mod_resource/content/1/Resilience%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resilience Fundamentals Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'building-resilience-in-the-workplace-module-1-resilience-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Building Career Resilience Module from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of five modules</strong> from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course and after completing all five modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Building Resilience in the Workplace Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Building Resilience in the Workplace </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4400/mod_resource/content/1/Building%20Career%20Resilience%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Building Career Resilience Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>habits of life long learners</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to cultivate strong professional relationships</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to take ownership of your career</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4407/mod_resource/content/1/Building%20Career%20Resilience%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Building Career Resilience Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'building-resilience-in-the-workplace-module-2-building-career-resilience';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Leadership and Resilience Module from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of five modules</strong> from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course and after completing all five modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Building Resilience in the Workplace Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Building Resilience in the Workplace </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4401/mod_resource/content/1/Leadership%20and%20Resilience%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leadership and Resilience Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to implement strategies to become a resilient leader</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability </strong>to lead through a challenge</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to build a resilient team</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4409/mod_resource/content/1/Leadership%20and%20Resilience%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leadership and Resilience Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'building-resilience-in-the-workplace-module-3-leadership-and-resilience';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Emotional and Physical Resilience Module from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of five modules</strong> from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course and after completing all five modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Building Resilience in the Workplace Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Building Resilience in the Workplace </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4402/mod_resource/content/1/Emotional%20%20Physical%20Resilience%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Emotional  Physical Resilience Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to boost resilience through self-awareness</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to increase your mental agility</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to boost your emotional self-regulation and resilience</li>\r\n<li><strong>Develop </strong>a healthy optimism</li>\r\n<li><strong>Maintain </strong>physical resilience</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4411/mod_resource/content/1/Emotional%20%20Physical%20Resilience%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Emotional  Physical Resilience Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'building-resilience-in-the-workplace-module-4-emotional-and-physical-resilience';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Thriving Through Challenges Module from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of five modules</strong> from the Building Resilience in the Workplace Course and after completing all five modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Building Resilience in the Workplace Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Building Resilience in the Workplace </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4403/mod_resource/content/1/Thriving%20Through%20Challenges%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Thriving Through Challenges Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>how to cope with challenges</li>\r\n<li><strong>Manage </strong>your response to workplace conflict</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>rest makes you more resilient</li>\r\n<li><strong>Adapt </strong>and become resilient</li>\r\n<li><strong>Step </strong>outside your comfort zone</li>\r\n<li><strong>Use </strong>criticism and rejection to your advantage and grow</li>\r\n<li><strong>Make Strategies </strong>for turning challenges into opportunities</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4413/mod_resource/content/1/Thriving%20Through%20Challenges%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Thriving Through Challenges Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'building-resilience-in-the-workplace-module-5-thriving-through-challenges';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Building Resilience in the Workplace Course</strong> has equipped you with the essential strategies and mindsets needed to stay grounded, strong, and effective in times of pressure or uncertainty. You explored foundational concepts of resilience, learned how to build career-long adaptability, and practiced methods for strengthening emotional and physical well-being. You also gained insights into how resilient leadership can support teams and how to turn challenges into opportunities for personal and professional growth.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final exam, reflect on the tools and techniques covered throughout each module — from managing stress and reframing setbacks to leading others with confidence and navigating workplace change. These resilience skills will support you throughout your career, helping you remain focused, adaptable, and empowered.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Completing this c</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">ourse demonstrates your readiness to thrive, grow, and lead with resilience in the modern workplace.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'building-resilience-in-the-workplace-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Course</strong>, a practical skills-building program designed to help you take control of your time, increase your productivity, and reduce stress in your daily life. Whether you are a student, professional, or business owner, mastering time management is essential for achieving your goals and performing at your best.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Throughout this course, you will explore the core principles of managing time effectively, setting meaningful goals, creating schedules that work, prioritizing tasks strategically, improving focus, and overcoming common time challenges. Each module provides practical techniques that you can apply immediately to your work and personal life.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to plan more intentionally, work more efficiently, and accomplish what truly matters with greater clarity and confidence.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of the <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Course</strong> is to help learners develop the habits, strategies, and systems required to manage their time effectively and achieve consistent results. This course aims to enable individuals to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Build disciplined routines</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Set and reach meaningful goals</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Increase productivity</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Reduce overwhelm and stress</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Make better decisions about how time is spent</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By combining theory with practical exercises, the course empowers learners to take full ownership of their daily habits and long-term outcomes.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand core time management principles: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain what time management is, why it matters, and which common habits affect productivity.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Set meaningful and achievable goals: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use goal-setting frameworks to define clear short-term and long-term goals that align with your personal and professional growth.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Build effective schedules and routines: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Create daily, weekly, and monthly plans that support discipline, focus, and consistent progress.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Apply prioritization strategies: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use methods such as the Eisenhower Matrix, ABC prioritization, and value-based ranking to identify what deserves your attention first.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Improve concentration and reduce distractions: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Enhance your focus using techniques such as time-blocking, deep work, habit stacking, and digital minimalism.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">6. Overcome common time challenges: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Identify obstacles such as procrastination, overload, interruptions, and lack of clarity—and apply strategies to manage them effectively.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'time-management-amp-prioritization-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Time Management Fundamentals Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4265/mod_resource/content/1/Time%20Management%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Time Management Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>time management</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to filter symptoms of poor time management</li>\r\n<li><strong>Manage </strong>your time effectively at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Track and analyze </strong>your time usage</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4272/mod_resource/content/1/Time%20Management%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Time Management Fundamentals Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'time-management-amp-prioritization-module-1-time-management-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Goal Setting Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4266/mod_resource/content/1/Goal%20Setting%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Goal Setting Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>is goal setting and why is it important</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to set goals that actually work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to stick to your goals</li>\r\n<li><strong>Measure </strong>and <strong>Track </strong>goal progress</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4275/mod_resource/content/1/Goal%20Setting%20Course%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Goal Setting Course Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'time-management-amp-prioritization-module-2-goal-setting';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Scheduling Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4267/mod_resource/content/1/Time%20Management%20Scheduling%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Time Management Scheduling Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the importance of scheduling and how to schedule your time</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to estimate the time needed to complete tasks</li>\r\n<li><strong>Use </strong>best good practice for time management scheduling </li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4274/mod_resource/content/1/Time%20Management%20Scheduling%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Time Management Scheduling Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'time-management-amp-prioritization-module-3-scheduling';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Prioritization Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4268/mod_resource/content/1/Time%20Management%20Prioritization%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Time Management Prioritization Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to prioritize tasks by urgency and importance</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to avoid the top six time-wasters in the workplace </li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand</strong> and manage procrastination</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4278/mod_resource/content/1/Time%20Management%20Prioritization%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Time Management Prioritization Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'time-management-amp-prioritization-module-4-prioritization';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Concentration Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4269/mod_resource/content/1/Time%20Management%20Concentration%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Time Management Concentration Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Create </strong>a distraction-free and productive work environment</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to adopt healthy habits to stay focused</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-why </strong>and <strong>how </strong>to stop multitasking</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to manage your energy and not your time</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4280/mod_resource/content/1/Time%20Management%20Concentration%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Time Management Concentration Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'time-management-amp-prioritization-module-5-concentration';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Overcoming Time Challenges Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Skills </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4270/mod_resource/content/1/Overcoming%20Challenges%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Overcoming Challenges Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to avoid taking on too much at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Manage </strong>distractions effectively</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to end the cycle of lateness</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>and <strong>why </strong>to cut back on meetings</li>\r\n<li><strong>Take </strong>control of your inbox</li>\r\n<li><strong>Adopt </strong>healthy habits to help you stay focused</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br><br></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4282/mod_resource/content/1/Overcoming%20Challenges%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Overcoming Challenges Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'time-management-amp-prioritization-module-6-overcoming-time-challenges';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Time Management &amp; Prioritization Course</strong> has equipped you with practical tools and strategies to organize your time, set clear goals, manage your workload, and stay focused on your most important priorities. You explored key topics such as time management fundamentals, goal setting, scheduling, prioritization, focus strategies, and overcoming time challenges.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final exam, reflect on the techniques you’ve learned and how they can help you become more productive, intentional, and disciplined in your daily life. Applying these skills consistently will enable you to work smarter, reduce stress, and achieve meaningful results.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to manage your time effectively and take control of your personal and professional success.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'time-management-amp-prioritization-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span>COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Problem Solving Techniques Course</strong>, a practical and engaging program designed to help you confidently navigate challenges in both the workplace and everyday life. Effective problem-solving is one of the most valuable skills in any career, enabling you to think clearly, analyze situations, make informed decisions, and contribute meaningfully to your team or organization.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Throughout this course, you will explore foundational problem-solving concepts, apply structured techniques to real scenarios, and learn how to approach challenges with creativity, logic, and resilience. Each module builds your capability step-by-step—from understanding the basics to mastering advanced problem-solving strategies used by top professionals.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end, you will have a toolkit of reliable methods that help you break down complex issues and implement solutions that work.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to equip learners with the knowledge, mindset, and tools needed to evaluate problems effectively and generate high-quality solutions. Whether you are a student, employee, supervisor, or business owner, this course empowers you to take initiative, think critically, and handle challenges with confidence.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The course also prepares you to contribute more effectively to projects, teams, and decision-making processes by improving your analytical thinking and structured reasoning skills.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the foundations of problem-solving: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Define what problem-solving is, why it matters, and recognise the characteristics of effective problem-solvers.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Apply problem-solving techniques in workplace scenarios: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify workplace challenges, assess root causes, and use appropriate strategies to address them.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Use structured steps to solve problems systematically: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Follow formal problem-solving frameworks such as:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Root cause analysis</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The 5 Whys</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Brainstorming</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Decision matrices</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">SWOT and other evaluation tools</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Implement advanced problem-solving approaches: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use creativity, innovation, and critical thinking to solve more complex or ambiguous issues.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Evaluate solutions and measure effectiveness: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Determine whether a solution works, monitor outcomes, and adjust your approach for continuous improvement.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'problem-solving-techniques-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Problem Solving Fundamentals Module from the Problem Solving Techniques Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of four modules</strong> from the Problem Solving Techniques Course and after completing all four modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Problem Solving Techniques Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Problem Solving Techniques</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p>\r\n<p><br><br></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4324/mod_resource/content/1/Problem%20Solving%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Problem Solving Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the fundamentals of problem solving</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to manage complicated problems</li>\r\n<li><strong>Form </strong>a team of top skills and implement strategies for effective problem solving</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to overcome barriers for effective problem solving</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to grow your problem solving skills</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4329/mod_resource/content/1/Problem%20Solving%20Fund%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Problem Solving Fund Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'problem-solving-techniques-module-1-problem-solving-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Problem Solving in the Workplace from the Problem Solving Techniques Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of four modules</strong> from the Problem Solving Techniques Course and after completing all four modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Problem Solving Techniques Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Problem Solving Techniques</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4325/mod_resource/content/1/Problem%20Solving%20in%20the%20Workplace%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Problem Solving in the Workplace Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Lead </strong>problem solving that will bring effective solutions</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to cultivate a culture that fosters creative problem solving</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to solve problems as a team</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to prioritize workplace problems</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4331/mod_resource/content/1/Problem%20Solving%20Steps%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Problem Solving Steps Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'problem-solving-techniques-module-2-problem-solving-in-the-workplace';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Steps to Problem Solving from the Problem Solving Techniques Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of four modules</strong> from the Problem Solving Techniques Course and after completing all four modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Problem Solving Techniques Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Problem Solving Techniques</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4326/mod_resource/content/1/Steps%20to%20Problem%20Solving%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Steps to Problem Solving Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to define a problem and identify its root cause</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to brainstorm solutions to a problem</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to research and evaluate possible solutions to problems</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> the best solution to problem</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to evaluate your results for your solutions to problems</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4333/mod_resource/content/1/Advanced%20Problem%20Solving%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Advanced Problem Solving Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'problem-solving-techniques-module-3-steps-to-problem-solving';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Advanced Problem-Solving from the Problem Solving Techniques Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of four modules</strong> from the Problem Solving Techniques Course and after completing all four modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Problem Solving Techniques Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Problem Solving Techniques</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4327/mod_resource/content/1/Advanced%20Problem%20Solving%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Advanced Problem Solving Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the divergent and convergent thinking</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to mitigate the risk of heuristics in problem solving</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to reframe problems for innovative solutions</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>design thinking compared to traditional problem solving</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4335/mod_resource/content/1/Advanced%20Problem%20Solving%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Advanced Problem Solving Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'problem-solving-techniques-module-4-advanced-problem-solving';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Problem Solving Techniques Course</strong> has guided you through the essential concepts, tools, and strategies needed to solve problems effectively and confidently. You learned the fundamentals of identifying problems, exploring solutions, and implementing structured steps to reach clear results. You also practiced applying advanced techniques that help you analyze situations more deeply, collaborate effectively, and make well-informed decisions in any environment.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on each framework and method covered in the modules. These techniques are practical and versatile—designed to help you succeed in your workplace, studies, and personal decision-making.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to approach challenges with clarity, structure, and confidence, enabling you to become a strong problem-solver in any setting.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'problem-solving-techniques-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Critical Thinking Strategies Course</strong>, a practical and empowering program designed to help you think more clearly, question assumptions, evaluate information, and make better decisions. In a world filled with constant information and rapid change, the ability to think critically is one of the most valuable skills for students, professionals, and leaders. This course will guide you step-by-step through the core principles of critical thinking, how to apply them in real workplace scenarios, and how to assess information with accuracy and confidence.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Through interactive examples, practical exercises, and relatable workplace situations, you will learn how to break down complex issues, avoid common thinking traps, and strengthen your reasoning skills. By the end of this course, critical thinking will become a natural part of how you analyze problems, communicate, and make decisions.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to strengthen learners’ ability to think analytically, logically, and independently when approaching challenges or evaluating information. This course equips you with the mindset and tools needed to identify bias, understand context, assess data quality, question assumptions, and form well-supported conclusions. Ultimately, the course empowers you to become a more effective problem-solver, communicator, and decision-maker in both personal and professional environments.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the foundations of critical thinking: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize what critical thinking is, why it matters, and how it contributes to better reasoning and decision-making.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Apply critical thinking techniques in workplace situations: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use structured thinking methods to evaluate workplace problems, assess risks, and make more informed decisions.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">\\3. Strengthen information literacy: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify credible sources, evaluate the quality of information, distinguish fact from opinion, and reduce the influence of bias and misinformation.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Analyze problems with a structured approach: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Break down complex issues into manageable parts, look for patterns, question assumptions, and apply logical reasoning.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Communicate ideas more clearly and persuasively: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support your conclusions with evidence, articulate your reasoning effectively, and engage in productive discussions.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'critical-thinking-strategies-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Critical Thinking Fundamentals Module from the Critical Thinking Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the Critical Thinking Strategies Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Critical Thinking Strategies Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Critical Thinking Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4366/mod_resource/content/1/Critical%20Thinking%20Fund%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Critical Thinking Fund Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the fundamentals of critical thinking and its process</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to ask better questions for critical thinking</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-when </strong>to use inductive or deductive reasoning</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to identify cognitive bias</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4370/mod_resource/content/1/Critical%20Thinking%20Fund%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Critical Thinking Fund Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'critical-thinking-strategies-module-1-critical-thinking-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Thinking in the Workplace Module from the Critical Thinking Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the Critical Thinking Strategies Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Critical Thinking Strategies Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Critical Thinking Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4367/mod_resource/content/1/Workplace%20Critical%20Thinking%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Workplace Critical Thinking Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to strengthen your critical thinking skills</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to build and strengthen workplace arguments</li>\r\n<li><strong>Help to develop </strong>other employees critical thinking skills</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to avoid workplace fallacies</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4372/mod_resource/content/1/Workplace%20Critical%20Thinking%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Workplace Critical Thinking Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'critical-thinking-strategies-module-2-thinking-in-the-workplace';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Critical Thinking and Information Literacy Module from the Critical Thinking Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the Critical Thinking Strategies Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Critical Thinking Strategies Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Critical Thinking Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4368/mod_resource/content/1/Critical%20Thinking%20%20Info%20Lit%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Critical Thinking  Info Lit Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to identify reliable information</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to distinguish between facts and opinion</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to identify satire and fake news </li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4374/mod_resource/content/1/Critical%20Thinking%20%20Info%20Lit%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Critical Thinking  Info Lit Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'critical-thinking-strategies-module-3-critical-thinking-and-information-literacy';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Critical Thinking Strategies Course</strong> has equipped you with essential thinking skills that help you evaluate information, make sound decisions, and approach workplace challenges with clarity and confidence. Throughout the modules, you explored critical thinking fundamentals, practiced applying structured thinking techniques in real workplace scenarios, and developed strong information literacy skills to navigate today’s fast-moving digital world.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on the methods you learned—such as questioning assumptions, analyzing evidence, identifying bias, and evaluating information sources. These skills will support your success in any professional environment and help you make informed, logical, and effective decisions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to think more clearly, reason more effectively, and approach problems with a strong critical-thinking mindset.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'critical-thinking-strategies-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Marketing Fundamentals Course</strong>, a comprehensive and practical introduction to the essential principles, tools, and strategies that drive successful modern marketing. Whether you are new to the field, strengthening your business skills, or preparing to support marketing functions in your organization, this course provides a complete foundation in understanding how brands communicate, attract customers, and grow in a competitive digital world.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Throughout this course, you will explore the full spectrum of marketing, from brand identity, customer insights, and product positioning, to content creation, digital marketing, paid advertising, SEO, and analytics. You will learn how to apply marketing strategies that are data-driven, customer-focused, and aligned with real business objectives.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will not only understand the core building blocks of marketing but also gain practical skills needed to create compelling brand messages, run digital campaigns, and make informed decisions that deliver measurable results.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of the <strong>Marketing Fundamentals Course</strong> is to equip learners with a strong foundation in both traditional and digital marketing principles. This course aims to help you understand how marketing works, why it is essential to business success, and how you can use marketing tools and strategies to build brand visibility and attract customers.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By combining theory, practical examples, and hands-on applications, this course prepares you to confidently contribute to marketing activities across any industry, whether you are part of a marketing team, starting a business, or enhancing your professional skill set.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Upon completing this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the core concepts of marketing: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain what marketing is, how it works, and why customer value drives all marketing decisions.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Build strong brand identity and strategy: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Develop brand messaging, positioning, and visual identity that resonates with target audiences.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Apply product marketing principles: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand product lifecycle, value propositions, and how to communicate features and benefits effectively.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Create engaging content for multiple channels: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Develop compelling content that aligns with brand goals and customer needs.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Conduct customer and marketing research: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Collect and analyze customer insights to guide marketing decisions and target the right audience.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">6. Understand website marketing foundations: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explore website strategy, user experience, landing pages, and conversion-focused design.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">7. Implement search engine optimization (SEO): </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use on-page and off-page SEO techniques to improve search ranking and organic visibility.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">8. Utilize social media marketing: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Create engaging social media campaigns that attract followers and drive brand engagement.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">9. Apply email marketing techniques: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Build email campaigns that nurture customer relationships and support sales.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">10. Plan and execute paid advertising campaigns: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use paid media platforms (Google, Meta, etc.) to target and convert customers effectively.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">11. Analyze marketing performance: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Interpret analytics data, measure campaign success, and make data-driven marketing decisions.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Marketing Fundamentals Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"></p>\r\n<p><br><br></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3615/mod_resource/content/1/Marketing%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Marketing Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the fundamentals of marketing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know </strong>the difference and value between traditional marketing and digital marketing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to apply the key elements of marketing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to develop a marketing plan</li>\r\n<li>Be <strong>capable </strong>of refining and understand your Unique Selling Point (USP)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the<strong> </strong>customer buying stages and how to stimulate them to create retention. </li>\r\n<li>Be <strong>capable </strong>of creating a <strong>Go-To-Market strategy</strong> that works from your marketing analytics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br><br></p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3627/mod_resource/content/1/Marketing%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Marketing Fundamentals Module Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3733/mod_resource/content/1/Module%201%20Marketing%20Fundamentals%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Module 1 Marketing Fundamentals Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-1-marketing-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Brand Identity and Strategy Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3616/mod_resource/content/1/Brand%20Identity%20and%20Strategy%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Brand Identity and Strategy Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand</strong> the importance of branding</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to develop your brand personality</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use visual brand design essentials</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to position and send a compelling message for your brand</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to tell a compelling brand story</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>a strategy for rebranding</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3629/mod_resource/content/1/Brand%20Identity%20and%20Strategy%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Brand Identity and Strategy Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3735/mod_resource/content/1/Module%202%20Brand%20Identity%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Module 2 Brand Identity Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-2-brand-identity-and-strategy';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Product Marketing Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3617/mod_resource/content/1/Product%20Marketing%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Product Marketing Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the market your product or service will operate into.</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to find and measure your Product-Market-Fit</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how</strong> to develop your Pricing Strategy</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to craft an effective Go-to-Market Strategy.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>steps to take for a successful product launch</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> strategies that will increase your sales.</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3631/mod_resource/content/1/Product%20Marketing%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Product Marketing Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3737/mod_resource/content/1/MODULE%203%20PRODUCT%20MARKETING%20SUMMARY.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MODULE 3 PRODUCT MARKETING SUMMARY.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-3-product-marketing';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Content Marketing Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3618/mod_resource/content/1/Content%20Marketing%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Content Marketing Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand</strong> content marketing and why you need it for your business</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to choose a suitable content distribution channel for your product or service</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to create content for your target audience</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to create your voice and tone in content marketing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Develop</strong> your content own strategy</li>\r\n<li><strong>Use</strong> marketing funnel tools to increase your buying customers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to create engaging content</li>\r\n<li><strong>Start </strong>your business blog</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3633/mod_resource/content/1/Content%20Marketing%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Content Marketing Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3741/mod_resource/content/1/Module%204%20Content%20Marketing%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Module 4 Content Marketing Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-4-content-marketing';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Customer and Marketing Research Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3619/mod_resource/content/1/Customer%20and%20Maketing%20Research%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer and Maketing Research Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the different types of customer research available</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to identify your target market</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to create and use buyer personas</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to create a customer journey map</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to conduct a competitive landscape analysis</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>a strategy to segment your target market</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3635/mod_resource/content/1/Customer%20and%20Marketing%20Research%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer and Marketing Research Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3766/mod_resource/content/1/Customer%20and%20Marketing%20Research%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Customer and Marketing Research Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-5-customer-and-marketing-research';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Website Marketing Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3620/mod_resource/content/1/Website%20Marketing%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website Marketing Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to use your website as a marketing tool to attract traffic</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to design great landing pages</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to reduce friction on your website and your website conversion rate</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3637/mod_resource/content/1/Website%20Marketing%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website Marketing Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3767/mod_resource/content/1/Website%20Marketing%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website Marketing Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-6-website-marketing';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Search Engine Optimization Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3621/mod_resource/content/1/Search%20Engine%20Optimisation%20%28SEO%29%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Search Engine Optimisation (SEO) Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the basics of Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to select keywords that will improve your SEO</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to optimize your website content to improve your SEO ranking</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>link building strategies for SEO</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how</strong> to structure your website for SEO</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to improve your image optimization for SEO</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3639/mod_resource/content/1/Search%20Engine%20Optimisation%20%28SEO%29%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Search Engine Optimisation (SEO) Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3768/mod_resource/content/1/Search%20Engine%20Optimization%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Search Engine Optimization Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-7-search-engine-optimization';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Social Media Marketing Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3622/mod_resource/content/1/Social%20Media%20Marketing%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Social Media Marketing Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>your social media strategy</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to choose the right social media channels based on your value offering</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use content buckets for social media organization and planning</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand</strong> the best social media practices for businesses </li>\r\n<li><strong>Get </strong><strong>started</strong> with social listening</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use hashtags for social media marketing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Boost </strong>your social media engagement</li>\r\n<li><strong>Capable </strong>of monitoring your social media metrics</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3641/mod_resource/content/1/Social%20Media%20Marketing%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Social Media Marketing Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3769/mod_resource/content/1/Social%20Media%20Marketing%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Social Media Marketing Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-8-social-media-marketing';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Email Marketing Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3623/mod_resource/content/1/Email%20Marketing%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Email Marketing Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong></li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to write effective marketing emails</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to avoid spam filters when sending emails</li>\r\n<li>have the <strong>capability</strong> write compelling email subject lines</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> audience segmentation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Design </strong>an effective email marketing campaign</li>\r\n<li><strong>know-how </strong>to craft high-performance marketing emails with A/B testing</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>email automation and understand the benefits</li>\r\n<li><strong>Capable </strong>of measuring the effectiveness of email marketing</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3643/mod_resource/content/1/Email%20Marketing%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Email Marketing Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3770/mod_resource/content/1/Email%20Marketing%20MODULE%20SUMMARY.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Email Marketing MODULE SUMMARY.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-9-email-marketing';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Paid Advertising Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3624/mod_resource/content/1/Paid%20Advertising%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Paid Advertising Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>how to use Search Engine Marketing (SEM) to your advantage</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to implement your paid search and paid per click advertising</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> out-of-home advertising</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> display advertising</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to create eye-catching display ads</li>\r\n<li><strong>Recapture </strong>audience attention through remarketing</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3645/mod_resource/content/1/Paid%20Advertising%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Paid Advertising Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3771/mod_resource/content/1/Paid%20Advertising%20Module%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Paid Advertising Module Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-10-paid-advertising';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Marketing Analytics Module</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT) that can be used to enrol on more courses.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong>Certificate of Completion</strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your Marketing Essentials<strong> </strong>Certificate of Completion, you can apply to be a <strong>Vow Support</strong> <strong>Marketing Essentials </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more <strong>Vow Rewards</strong><strong> Tokens</strong> (VRT).</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3625/mod_resource/content/1/Marketing%20Analytics%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Marketing Analytics Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>what is marketing analytics and how you can use it to your advantage</li>\r\n<li><strong>Choose </strong>marketing key performance indicators from your marketing campaign</li>\r\n<li><strong>Capable</strong> of measuring the effectiveness of your marketing campaign</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to interpret and analyze the marketing data</li>\r\n<li><strong>Use </strong>storytelling to communicate data</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3647/mod_resource/content/2/Marketing%20Analytics%20Module%20Reading%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Marketing Analytics Module Reading Material.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/3773/mod_resource/content/1/Marketing%20Analytics%20Module%20Summary.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Marketing Analytics Module Summary.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-module-11-marketing-analytics';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Marketing Fundamentals Course</strong> has provided you with a strong foundation in the core principles and modern practices of marketing. You explored key topics including brand identity, product marketing, customer research, content marketing, SEO, social media, email marketing, paid advertising, website marketing, and analytics. Each module gave you practical tools and frameworks to attract, engage, and convert customers across different channels.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">You are now prepared to apply marketing strategies in real business environments, contribute to marketing campaigns, and make informed decisions based on customer insights and performance data. As you complete the final exam, reflect on how these skills will support your career growth or business goals. Successful completion of this course demonstrates your readiness to think like a marketer—strategic, creative, analytical, and customer-focused.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'marketing-fundamentals-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Leadership Development Course</strong>, a practical and empowering program designed to help you understand what leadership truly means and how to apply it confidently in the modern workplace. Leadership is not defined by a job title — it is a skill set that anyone can develop. Whether you are leading a team, contributing to projects, or preparing for future opportunities, strong leadership abilities help you influence others, make sound decisions, and guide teams toward shared goals.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">In this course, you will explore the core principles of effective leadership, discover different leadership styles, develop emotional intelligence, and learn how to navigate high-pressure situations through strong crisis management techniques. Each module equips you with real-world strategies you can apply immediately, regardless of your industry or experience level.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to help learners develop the mindset, confidence, and practical skills required to lead effectively in any environment. You will learn how to inspire others, build trust, communicate with clarity, and respond professionally to workplace challenges. By building your emotional intelligence and crisis management capabilities, you will be better prepared to lead teams, drive performance, and contribute meaningfully to organizational success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course is designed for students, professionals, supervisors, aspiring managers, and entrepreneurs who want to become stronger, more resilient, and more influential leaders.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand leadership essentials: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain what leadership is, identify key leadership traits, and understand how leaders influence individuals and teams.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Recognize and apply different leadership styles: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify various leadership styles (such as transformational, democratic, and situational leadership) and choose the most effective approach for different workplace situations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Strengthen emotional intelligence (EQ): </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Improve self-awareness, regulate emotions, build empathy, and communicate with clarity to lead more effectively.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Lead confidently during crises: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply crisis management principles to respond to challenges, make decisions under pressure, and maintain team stability during uncertain times.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Demonstrate practical leadership in real scenarios: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use the tools learned to improve team performance, handle conflict, support others, and lead with confidence and integrity.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'leadership-development-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Leadership Fundamentals Module from the Leadership Development Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of four modules</strong> from the <strong>Leadership Development </strong>Course and after completing all four modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leadership Development</strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leadership Development </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4492/mod_resource/content/1/Leadership%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leadership Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>what makes a good leader</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to engage and motivate employees as a leader</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to lead your team with a vision</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to become a better leader</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4497/mod_resource/content/1/Leadership%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leadership Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leadership-development-module-1-leadership-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Leadership Styles Module from the Leadership Development Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of four modules</strong> from the <strong>Leadership Development </strong>Course and after completing all four modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leadership Development</strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leadership Development </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4493/mod_resource/content/1/Leadership%20Styles%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leadership Styles Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>different types of leadership styles that can boost performance.</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to implement different leadership styles</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-when </strong>to use each leadership style</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to use each leadership style</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4499/mod_resource/content/1/Leadership%20Styles%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leadership Styles Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leadership-development-module-2-leadership-styles';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Emotional Intelligence Module from the Leadership Development Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of four modules</strong> from the <strong>Leadership Development </strong>Course and after completing all four modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leadership Development</strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leadership Development </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4494/mod_resource/content/1/Emotional%20Intelligence%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Emotional Intelligence Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>what is Emotional Intelligence (EQ)</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to implement strategies that will boost your Self-regulation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to improve your Self-awareness</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to increase your Self-Motivation and develop empathy</li>\r\n<li><strong>Improve and Hence </strong>your Social Skills</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4501/mod_resource/content/1/Emotional%20Intelligence%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Emotional Intelligence Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leadership-development-module-3-emotional-intelligence';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Crisis Management Module from the Leadership Development Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of four modules</strong> from the <strong>Leadership Development </strong>Course and after completing all four modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leadership Development</strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leadership Development </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4495/mod_resource/content/1/Crisis%20Management%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Crisis Management Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand</strong> what is crisis and how to manage it</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know</strong> and differentiate between different types of business crisis</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to prevent and prepare for a crisis</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to respond to a crisis</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> a recovery plan after a crisis</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4503/mod_resource/content/1/Crisis%20Management%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Crisis Management Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leadership-development-module-4-crisis-management';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Leadership Development Course</strong> has equipped you with a strong foundation of leadership knowledge, covering essential skills such as leadership fundamentals, leadership styles, emotional intelligence, and crisis management. You explored what makes leadership effective, how different styles influence teams, how emotional intelligence strengthens relationships, and how leaders respond to high-pressure or unexpected challenges.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final exam, reflect on the strategies and principles you learned in each module. Effective leadership is a continuous journey of self-awareness, communication, adaptability, and responsibility. The tools and techniques from this course are designed to support you throughout your career, helping you grow as a leader in any role or environment.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to lead with confidence, motivate others, make informed decisions, and navigate challenges with resilience and clarity.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'leadership-development-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Team Management Strategies Course</strong>, a practical and comprehensive program designed to equip you with the essential skills needed to lead, support, and develop high-performing teams in modern workplaces. Effective team management requires more than assigning tasks — it involves understanding people, building trust, fostering communication, and creating an environment where individuals and teams can thrive. This course provides step-by-step guidance to help you become a confident and capable team leader, whether you are new to management or looking to strengthen your existing leadership skills.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Throughout the modules, you will explore the foundations of team management, learn how to support new managers, understand team dynamics, build strong team cultures, and lead teams both in-person and remotely. You’ll also gain practical strategies for motivation, conflict resolution, performance management, and navigating challenging responsibilities such as letting an employee go.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to develop skilled and adaptable team leaders who can manage people effectively, communicate with clarity, build strong workplace relationships, and drive team performance. This course helps learners understand how to motivate diverse individuals, address challenges professionally, strengthen team culture, and make informed decisions that support organizational success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Whether you are a supervisor, aspiring team leader, project coordinator, or current manager, this course empowers you with the tools and techniques needed to lead teams confidently and compassionately.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand core principles of team management: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain the fundamentals of effective team management, leadership roles, and expectations of a team leader.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Support new managers and transitions into leadership: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize the challenges new managers face and apply strategies to build confidence and competence in leadership roles.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Develop and grow team members: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Provide coaching, constructive feedback, performance guidance, and development opportunities that support individual and team growth.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Build strong and positive team cultures: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Foster collaboration, inclusivity, accountability, and trust within your team.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Delegate tasks effectively: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Assign responsibilities based on strengths, skill levels, and workload distribution while maintaining accountability.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">6. Motivate and inspire your team: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply motivational strategies that increase engagement, improve morale, and boost productivity.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">7. Lead remote and hybrid teams successfully: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use communication, tools, and leadership strategies to support effective collaboration across distance.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">8. Understand team dynamics: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize different team roles, behaviors, and interaction patterns to improve teamwork and performance.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">9. Manage performance with confidence: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Set clear expectations, track progress, deliver feedback, and support improvement.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">10. Resolve conflict professionally: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify sources of conflict and apply constructive strategies to promote understanding and resolution.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">11. Handle difficult responsibilities respectfully: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Navigate sensitive situations—such as letting an employee go—with professionalism, fairness, and empathy.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Team Management Fundamentals Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4535/mod_resource/content/1/Team%20Management%20Fundamentals.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Team Management Fundamentals.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the fundamentals of team management</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>makes a team effective</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to communicate with your team effectively</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>team management techniques</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to avoid common team problems</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4568/mod_resource/content/1/Team%20Management%20Fund%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Team Management Fund Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-1-team-management-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to New Manager Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4537/mod_resource/content/1/New%20Manager%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">New Manager Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Transition </strong>from employee to manager position</li>\r\n<li><strong>Avoid </strong>new manager mistake</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to transition from peer to boss</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to manage people with more experience than you</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4575/mod_resource/content/1/New%20Manager%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">New Manager Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-2-new-manager';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Developing your Team Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4539/mod_resource/content/1/Developing%20your%20Team%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Developing your Team Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>a manager\'s role in career development</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to implement team development in stages</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to conduct a gap analysis</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to choose the right training methods</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to conduct effective one-on-ones</li>\r\n<li><strong>Develop </strong>your team through coaching</li>\r\n<li><strong>Get </strong>to know employees strength, interest and what they value</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4581/mod_resource/content/1/Developing%20your%20Team%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Developing your Team Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-3-developing-your-team';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Team Culture Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4552/mod_resource/content/1/Team%20Culture%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Team Culture Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module</strong><strong>, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>team culture and why it matters</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to assess your team culture</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to create a strengths-based culture</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to build a positive team culture</li>\r\n<li><strong>Transform</strong> a negative team culture </li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4590/mod_resource/content/1/Team%20Culture%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Team Culture Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-4-team-culture';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Delegating Tasks Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4560/mod_resource/content/1/Delegating%20Tasks%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Delegating Tasks Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the importance of delegating</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-why </strong>people don\'t delegate</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>and <strong>how </strong>to delegate</li>\r\n<li><strong>Delegate </strong>the right tasks to the right people</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to keep control of employees without micromanaging</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4598/mod_resource/content/1/Delegating%20Task%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Delegating Task Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-5-delegating-tasks';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Motivating your Team Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4561/mod_resource/content/1/Motivating%20your%20Team%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Motivating your Team Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>factors that influence motivation</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to improve employees job satisfaction to increase motivation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> strategies to motivate employee </li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4605/mod_resource/content/1/Motivating%20your%20Team%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Motivating your Team Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-6-motivating-your-team';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Managing Remote Teams Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4562/mod_resource/content/1/Managing%20Remote%20Teams%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Managing Remote Teams Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to hire exceptional remote talent</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement best practices for managing remote teams</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to communicate with remote teams</li>\r\n<li><strong>Increase</strong> accountability to your remote teams</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to keep remote workers connected</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4614/mod_resource/content/1/Managing%20Remote%20Teams%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Managing Remote Teams Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-7-managing-remote-teams';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Team Dynamics Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4563/mod_resource/content/1/Team%20Dynamics%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Team Dynamics Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>what is team dynamics and why it matters</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to adopt common roles in a team</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-the </strong>characteristics of high performance teams</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to Improve team dynamics performance</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand</strong> and leverage different work styles</li>\r\n<li><strong>Manage </strong>the multigenerational workplace</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4622/mod_resource/content/1/Team%20Dynamics%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Team Dynamics Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-8-team-dynamics';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Performance Management Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4564/mod_resource/content/1/Performance%20Management%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Performance Management Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>performance management</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to improve poor performance</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to develop a performance improvement plan</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to manage high performers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Conduct </strong>effective performance reviews</li>\r\n<li><strong>Give </strong>effective employee feedback</li>\r\n<li><strong>Handle </strong>difficult reactions to feedback</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to effectively manage managers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>continuous performance management</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4630/mod_resource/content/1/Performance%20Management%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Performance Management Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-9-performance-management';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Resolving Conflict Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4565/mod_resource/content/1/Resolving%20Conflict%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resolving Conflict Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>common causes of conflict in the workplace</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>people deal with conflict</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to implement steps to mediate conflict between employees</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> conflict resolution techniques</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to deal with frustrated or angry employees</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to deal with abusive behaviour  </li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4641/mod_resource/content/1/Resolving%20Conflict%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resolving Conflict Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-10-resolving-conflict';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Letting an Employee Go Module from the Team Management Strategies Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of eleven modules</strong> from the <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong> Course and after completing all eleven modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong> Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Team Management Strategies</strong><strong> </strong><strong> </strong><strong>Mentor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4566/mod_resource/content/1/Letting%20an%20Employee%20Go%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Letting an Employee Go Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>good reasons for letting an employee go</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> steps to take before letting an employee go</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to tell an employee they\'re fired</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to mitigate legal risks when letting an employee go</li>\r\n<li><strong>Reassure </strong>your team after someone is let go</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4649/mod_resource/content/1/Letting%20an%20Employee%20Go%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Letting an Employee Go Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-module-11-letting-an-employee-go';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Team Management Strategies Course</strong> has provided you with the foundational knowledge and practical skills needed to lead teams with confidence, clarity, and compassion. Through topics such as leadership fundamentals, team culture, motivation, delegation, performance management, and conflict resolution, you have developed a strong understanding of what it means to manage people effectively. You also explored modern leadership challenges, including managing remote teams and navigating difficult situations such as employee termination.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on the tools, strategies, and principles learned across all modules. Effective team management requires communication, empathy, decision-making, and the ability to support your team through change and challenges. These skills will help you build strong teams, improve collaboration, enhance performance, and grow as a leader.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to lead teams confidently and contribute meaningfully to organizational success.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'team-management-strategies-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Leading Through Change Course</strong>, a practical and empowering program designed to help you understand, manage, and lead change confidently within any organization. Change is constant—new technologies, restructuring, shifting markets, and evolving expectations all require leaders who can guide teams through transformation with clarity, empathy, and strategic focus. This course provides a complete introduction to the principles of change management, as well as the leadership skills needed to support people through transitions and build resilience across teams.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Throughout this course, you will explore change management models, understand the full change process, practice effective communication techniques, and learn how to lead with confidence in both everyday change and crisis situations. Whether you are a manager, aspiring leader, or team member who wants to strengthen your influence, this course equips you with the tools to navigate change successfully.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to develop strong, adaptive leaders who can guide people through change in a supportive, structured, and strategic way. You will learn how to analyze change, plan transitions, address resistance, communicate effectively, and ensure long-term adoption of new processes and behaviors. The course helps learners build the mindset and skills required to lead confidently during both planned changes and unexpected crises.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course prepares you to succeed in dynamic, fast-paced work environments and strengthens your ability to support your team through uncertainty.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the foundations of change management: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Describe what change management is, why it matters, and how it impacts individuals and organizations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Apply structured change management models: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use models such as ADKAR, Lewin’s Change Model, and Kotter’s 8-Step Process to plan and support successful transitions.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Navigate the change management process: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand each phase of the change journey—from preparing for change to implementing and sustaining long-term results.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Communicate change effectively: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Craft clear, supportive, and engaging communication that reduces resistance, builds trust, and aligns teams with organizational goals.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Lead teams through change with confidence: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use empathetic leadership, coaching, and strong decision-making to guide individuals and teams through uncertain or challenging periods.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">6. Manage change during crises: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply crisis management principles to lead with calmness, clarity, and stability in high-pressure or unexpected change situations.</span></p>' WHERE slug = 'leading-through-change-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Change Management Fundamentals Module from the Leading Through Change Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leading Through Change </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4684/mod_resource/content/1/Change%20Management%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Change Management Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the fundamentals of change management</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability </strong>to implement organizational change</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the basics of change management models</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>best practices for change management</li>\r\n<li><strong>Overcome </strong>common change management challenges</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4692/mod_resource/content/1/Change%20Management%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Change Management Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leading-through-change-module-1-change-management-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Change Management Models Module from the Leading Through Change Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leading Through Change </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4685/mod_resource/content/1/Change%20Management%20Models%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Change Management Models Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module</strong><strong>, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>and implement<strong> </strong>the McKinsey model</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> Lewin\'s 3-step Change Management model</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>Kotter\'s 8-step change model</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>Kubler-Ross change management framework</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>the Satir change management model</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4694/mod_resource/content/1/Change%20Management%20Models%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Change Management Models Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leading-through-change-module-2-change-management-models';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to The Change Management Process Module from the Leading Through Change Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leading Through Change </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4688/mod_resource/content/1/Change%20Management%20Process%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Change Management Process Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand</strong> the change management process</li>\r\n<li><strong>Make </strong>the case for change</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how</strong> to develop and communicate a vision for change</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to create a change action plan</li>\r\n<li><strong>Assist </strong>employees facing change at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to measure effectiveness of change</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4697/mod_resource/content/1/Change%20Management%20Process%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Change Management Process Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leading-through-change-module-3-the-change-management-process';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Communicating Change Module from the Leading Through Change Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leading Through Change </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4687/mod_resource/content/1/Communicating%20Change%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Communicating Change Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to plan an effective change communication strategy</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to get employee buy-in during change</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>an effective change management communication.</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4696/mod_resource/content/1/Communicating%20Change%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Communicating Change Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leading-through-change-module-4-communicating-change';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Leading Through Change Module from the Leading Through Change Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leading Through Change </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4689/mod_resource/content/1/Fundamentals%20of%20Leading%20Through%20Change%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fundamentals of Leading Through Change Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module</strong><strong>, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the fundamentals of leading through change</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to lead teams through change</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to empower employees to successfully navigate change</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4700/mod_resource/content/1/Fundamentals%20of%20Leading%20through%20Change%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fundamentals of Leading through Change Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leading-through-change-module-5-leading-through-change';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Managing Change in Time of Crisis Module from the Leading Through Change Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Leading Through Change </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Leading Through Change </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4690/mod_resource/content/1/Managing%20Change%20in%20time%20of%20Crisis%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Managing Change in time of Crisis Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Lead</strong> during an unexpected change</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to build adaptability for your team </li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to support your employees in a crisis</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to turn a crisis situation into an opportunity for positive change</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4702/mod_resource/content/1/Managing%20Change%20in%20Crisis%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Managing Change in Crisis Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'leading-through-change-module-6-managing-change-in-time-of-crisis';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Leading Through Change Course</strong> has given you the essential tools and strategies to guide individuals and organizations successfully through transitions. You have explored the foundations of change management, studied leading change models, learned the step-by-step change process, and developed communication methods that reduce resistance and build engagement. In addition, you gained valuable skills in leading teams through uncertainty and managing change during times of crisis.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on how each module has strengthened your ability to plan, communicate, and lead change effectively. These skills will support your growth as a leader and help you navigate evolving workplace challenges with confidence and clarity.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to become a strong, adaptable, and supportive change leader in any environment.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'leading-through-change-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness Course</strong>, a powerful and supportive program designed to help individuals strengthen their emotional well-being, build healthy habits, and create a positive mindset at work and in daily life. In a world where stress, pressure, and change are constant, mental health is essential for personal happiness, productivity, and long-term success. This course provides practical tools, engaging insights, and science-based wellness strategies that anyone can use to develop resilience, manage emotions, and enhance overall wellness.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Throughout the modules, you will learn the foundations of positive psychology, explore how to build and sustain healthy habits, understand the role of physical activity, and gain awareness of mental health needs in the workplace. You will also develop skills for navigating emotions constructively and contributing to a work culture that prioritizes well-being.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to promote healthier, happier, and more balanced individuals by empowering learners with practical mental wellness strategies they can apply in both their professional and personal lives. The course aims to strengthen emotional intelligence, reduce stress, and build positive behaviors that support long-term mental and physical well-being. It also encourages the development of supportive workplace environments where mental health is understood, respected, and openly discussed.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course is valuable for employees, students, leaders, and anyone seeking to improve their mental resilience and cultivate a healthier lifestyle.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the foundations of positive psychology: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain key concepts such as mindfulness, gratitude, optimism, and well-being, and understand their impact on mental health.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Build and maintain healthy habits: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Develop practical routines that support emotional, physical, and mental wellness in everyday life.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Apply positive psychology in the workplace: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize how positive behaviors improve productivity, teamwork, motivation, and workplace satisfaction.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Enhance wellness through physical activity: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand the connection between exercise, stress reduction, mood improvement, and energy levels.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Improve mental health awareness; </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify signs of stress, burnout, or emotional strain and learn how to respond to mental health needs with care.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">6. Manage emotions effectively: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Use emotional regulation strategies to stay grounded, manage difficult emotions, and respond thoughtfully in challenging situations.</span></p>' WHERE slug = 'employee-mental-health-amp-wellness-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Positive Psychology Fundamentals Module from the Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4746/mod_resource/content/1/Positive%20Psychology%20Fundamentals%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Positive Psychology Fundamentals Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the science of happiness and well-being</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to improve your wellbeing through social connections</li>\r\n<li><strong>Challenge</strong> core beliefs</li>\r\n<li><strong>Avoid </strong>cognitive distortions that undermine your happiness</li>\r\n<li><strong>Adopt </strong>physical habits for happiness and well-being</li>\r\n<li><strong>Find </strong>purpose and meaning in life</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to connect with nature and improve health</li>\r\n<li><strong>Boost </strong>your happiness</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4753/mod_resource/content/1/Positve%20Psych%20Fund%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Positve Psych Fund Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'employee-mental-health-amp-wellness-module-1-positive-psychology-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Forming Healthy Habits Module from the Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4747/mod_resource/content/1/Forming%20Healthy%20Habits%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Forming Healthy Habits Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the relationship between pressure and performance</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to manage your stress and increase mental focus</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to perform well under pressure</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to recover from burnout</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4759/mod_resource/content/1/Forming%20Healthy%20Habits%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Forming Healthy Habits Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'employee-mental-health-amp-wellness-module-2-forming-healthy-habits';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Positive Psychology in the Workplace Module from the Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4748/mod_resource/content/1/Positive%20Psychology%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Positive Psychology Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>makes people feel happy and fulfilled at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to find meaning and purpose in your work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Build </strong>a healthy social life at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Boost </strong>your wellness with healthy workplace habits </li>\r\n<li><strong>Find </strong>flow and engagement in your work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Foster </strong>positive emotions at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to combat workplace perfectionism</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4760/mod_resource/content/1/Positive%20Psychology%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Positive Psychology Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'employee-mental-health-amp-wellness-module-3-positive-psychology-in-the-workplace';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Exercise Module from the Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4749/mod_resource/content/1/Exercise%20Course%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Exercise Course Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Master </strong>a beginners exercise</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to build a sustainable workout habit</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to apply the FITT principle to your workouts</li>\r\n<li><strong>Overcome </strong>reasons of not exercising </li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> easy desk stretches </li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4761/mod_resource/content/1/Exercise%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Exercise Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'employee-mental-health-amp-wellness-module-4-exercise';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Mental Health Awareness Module from the Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4750/mod_resource/content/1/Mental%20Health%20Awareness%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mental Health Awareness Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to support your team\'s mental health</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to raise awareness, supporting co-workers with mental health</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to combat stigma and misconceptions about mental health</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to recognize the signs of employee substance abuse at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Guide</strong> support to grieving employees</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to support a grieving co-worker</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4762/mod_resource/content/1/Mental%20Health%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mental Health Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'employee-mental-health-amp-wellness-module-5-mental-health-awareness';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Dealing with Emotions Module from the Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of six modules</strong> from the <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course and after completing all six modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4751/mod_resource/content/1/Dealing%20With%20Emotions%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Dealing With Emotions Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>your brain on uncertainty</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to handle big emotions</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to grieve the death of a co-worker</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to find a good therapist</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the anger cycle and how to interrupt it</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how</strong> to get out of a mental rut</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4763/mod_resource/content/1/Dealing%20with%20Emotions%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Dealing with Emotions Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'employee-mental-health-amp-wellness-module-6-dealing-with-emotions';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Employee Mental Health &amp; Wellness Course</strong> has equipped you with essential knowledge and practical strategies to improve your emotional well-being, build healthier habits, and contribute to a more positive and supportive workplace environment. You explored the foundations of positive psychology, learned how habits influence behavior, discovered the importance of exercise for mental health, and developed skills for understanding and managing emotions. You also gained insights into workplace mental health awareness and how to support yourself and others through wellness challenges.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on the tools and insights gained in each module. These strategies will help you reduce stress, strengthen your mental resilience, and live with greater balance and clarity—both at work and beyond.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Completing this course demonstrates your commitment to personal wellness and your readiness to promote a healthier, more positive workplace for yourself and others.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'employee-mental-health-amp-wellness-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Stress Management Techniques Course</strong>, a practical and supportive program designed to help you understand stress, how it affects your life, and how to manage it effectively. Stress is a natural part of daily life, but when left unmanaged, it can impact your health, work performance, relationships, and overall well-being. This course provides a clear and simple guide to understanding stress triggers, recognizing warning signs, and applying practical strategies to reduce and regulate stress in both personal and professional environments.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Through relatable content, real-life examples, and easy-to-follow techniques, you will learn how to take control of stress, stay balanced, and build healthier long-term habits that support emotional and physical well-being.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to help learners develop the awareness, knowledge, and practical skills needed to manage stress effectively. By understanding how stress works and learning techniques to regulate it, you will be able to improve your focus, productivity, mental clarity, and emotional resilience. The course also aims to empower individuals to build healthier habits, cope better with workplace demands, and maintain a strong sense of well-being.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course is beneficial for students, employees, leaders, or anyone navigating daily pressures or looking for personalized stress-relief strategies.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the fundamentals of stress: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify what stress is, its causes, and how it affects your body, mind, and behavior.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Recognize the impact of stress on work performance: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain how stress influences productivity, concentration, communication, decision-making, and workplace relationships.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Develop personalized stress-relief strategies: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply a range of practical methods—such as breathing exercises, mindfulness, time management, physical activities, and relaxation techniques—to reduce stress.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Strengthen emotional resilience: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Build coping mechanisms that help you stay calm and focused during challenging moments or high-pressure situations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Establish long-term wellness habits: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Create routines that promote overall well-being, reduce stress buildup, and improve your mental and emotional health.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'stress-management-techniques-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Stress Fundamentals Module from the Stress Management Techniques Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4818/mod_resource/content/1/Stress%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stress Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the fundamental causes of stress</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to manage your body reaction to stress</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to identify and manage your stress triggers</li>\r\n<li><strong>Differentiate </strong>between good stress and bad stress</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4822/mod_resource/content/1/Stress%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stress Fundamentals Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'stress-management-techniques-module-1-stress-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Stress and Work Performance Module from the Stress Management Techniques Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4819/mod_resource/content/1/Stress%20and%20Work%20Performance%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stress and Work Performance Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the relationship between pressure and performance</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to manage your stress and increase mental focus</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to perform well under pressure</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to recover from burnout</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4824/mod_resource/content/1/Stress%20and%20Work%20Performance%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stress and Work Performance Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'stress-management-techniques-module-2-stress-and-work-performance';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Strategies to Relieve Stress Module from the Stress Management Techniques Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Stress Management Techniques </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4820/mod_resource/content/1/Strategies%20to%20Relieve%20Stress%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Strategies to Relieve Stress Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>strategies for coping with stress</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to guide others to meditation for stress management</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to exercise for stress relief</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to reduce stress by changing your thinking</li>\r\n<li><strong>Journal</strong> for stress relief</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>relaxation techniques for stress relief</li>\r\n<li><strong>Cultivate </strong>an internal locus of control</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>sensory based strategies for reducing stress quickly</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4826/mod_resource/content/1/Strategies%20to%20Relieve%20Stress%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Strategies to Relieve Stress Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'stress-management-techniques-module-3-strategies-to-relieve-stress';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Stress Management Techniques Course</strong> has provided you with essential insights and practical tools to understand, manage, and reduce stress in daily life. Through the modules, you explored the fundamentals of stress, learned how stress affects work performance, and discovered a variety of strategies to relieve and prevent stress buildup. These techniques enable you to improve your focus, maintain emotional balance, and approach challenges with clarity and resilience.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on the techniques that resonated with you and consider how they can support your ongoing well-being. Consistent practice will allow you to reduce stress more effectively and build healthier habits that contribute to long-term personal and professional success.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to manage stress proactively and maintain a healthier, more balanced lifestyle.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'stress-management-techniques-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Workplace Compliance Essentials Course</strong>, a practical and safety-focused program designed to help learners understand and follow essential workplace compliance standards. Every organization must ensure that its employees work in a safe, respectful, and legally compliant environment. This course introduces the foundational rules, responsibilities, and behaviors that support workplace safety, protect employees, and reduce risks.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Through engaging lessons and real-world examples, you will learn how to maintain a safe workspace, respond to potential hazards, prevent workplace violence, and recognize situations that may compromise safety or well-being. Whether you are an employee, supervisor, or business owner, this course equips you with essential compliance knowledge required for safe and ethical workplace operations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to promote safe, compliant, and respectful workplaces by helping learners understand key compliance principles, safety procedures, and protective behaviors. The course aims to reduce workplace accidents, strengthen organizational safety culture, and ensure that individuals can confidently identify risks and respond appropriately.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course prepares learners to follow safety guidelines, uphold regulatory standards, and contribute to a secure and professional work environment.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand core workplace health and safety principles: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain why workplace safety is important and identify key safety responsibilities for both employees and employers.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Identify workplace hazards: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize physical, environmental, and behavioral risks that may cause injury, harm, or unsafe conditions.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Follow preventive safety practices: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply basic safety procedures, proper equipment handling, and hazard reporting methods to reduce accidents.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Understand workplace violence risks: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify different types of workplace violence, early warning signs, and common risk factors.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Respond appropriately to unsafe situations: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Demonstrate safe behaviors, de-escalation techniques, and appropriate reporting procedures when facing potential violence or harmful behavior.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">6. Support a safety-focused workplace culture: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Promote responsibility, awareness, teamwork, and compliance with safety rules and organizational policies.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'workplace-compliance-essentials-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to  Workplace Health &amp; Safety Module from the Workplace Compliance Essentials Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of two modules</strong> from the <strong>Workplace Compliance Essentials </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Workplace Compliance Essentials </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Workplace Compliance Essentials </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4854/mod_resource/content/1/Workplace%20Health%20Safety%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Workplace Health Safety Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>OSH Act for construction hazard</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement</strong> ergonomics, safe lifting, pushing and pulling safety measures</li>\r\n<li><strong>Reduce </strong>slips, trips and falls</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to implement ergonomics measures at the office and at home</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong> eye safety fundamentals in the workplace</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>ladder safety fundamentals</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4857/mod_resource/content/1/Workplace%20Health%20Safety%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Workplace Health Safety Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'workplace-compliance-essentials-module-1-workplace-health-amp-safety';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to  Workplace Violence Module from the Workplace Compliance Essentials Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of two modules</strong> from the <strong>Workplace Compliance Essentials </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Workplace Compliance Essentials </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Workplace Compliance Essentials </strong><strong> M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4855/mod_resource/content/1/Workplace%20Violence%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Workplace Violence Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>workplace violence and its impact</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how</strong> to identify and report early warning sings of workplace violence</li>\r\n<li><strong>Recognize </strong>and neutralize workplace bullying</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>levels of workplace bullying and how to respond to them</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to respond to active shooter threat</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability </strong>to respond to a first aid for life-threatening bleeding</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4859/mod_resource/content/1/Workplace%20Violence%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Workplace Violence Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'workplace-compliance-essentials-module-2-workplace-violence';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Workplace Compliance Essentials Course</strong> has equipped you with fundamental knowledge and skills to help maintain a safe, respectful, and compliant work environment. You explored key concepts in workplace health and safety, learned how to identify hazards, and gained strategies to prevent accidents and ensure safe practices. You also developed an understanding of workplace violence, including how to recognize risks and what steps to take to protect yourself and others.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, take time to reflect on the safety guidelines, compliance responsibilities, and protective strategies discussed in each module. These practices will support you in maintaining a secure work environment and contributing to an organization that prioritizes safety and well-being.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to uphold workplace compliance standards and support a culture of responsibility, safety, and respect.</span></p>' WHERE slug = 'workplace-compliance-essentials-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Business Ethics in Practice Course</strong>, an essential program designed to strengthen ethical awareness, decision-making, and professional conduct in the workplace. Ethical behavior is the foundation of trust, credibility, and long-term success in every organization. This course introduces the core principles of business ethics and explores how leaders and employees can apply ethical standards to guide their actions, strengthen workplace culture, and ensure responsible business practices.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Through practical examples, real-world scenarios, and reflective activities, you will learn how ethical principles influence daily decisions, how leaders set the tone for ethical behavior, and how employees play a crucial role in upholding organizational values.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to equip learners with the knowledge and tools needed to recognize ethical issues, make informed decisions, and promote integrity within their professional environments. By understanding the responsibilities of leaders and employees in building ethical workplaces, learners will be better prepared to foster trust, accountability, fairness, and compliance in their organizations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course empowers individuals at all levels—from students to managers—to apply ethical thinking consistently in their work and interactions.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the fundamentals of business ethics: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Define business ethics, identify common ethical principles, and explain their importance in organizational success and public trust.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Evaluate ethical dilemmas in the workplace: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize ethical challenges, analyze potential consequences, and apply structured methods to guide responsible decision-making.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Understand the role of leadership in ethics: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain how leaders influence organizational values, model ethical behavior, and create cultures where integrity is expected and rewarded.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Apply ethical behavior in employee responsibilities: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand the expectations for ethical conduct, compliance, professionalism, and accountability in everyday workplace interactions.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Strengthen organizational ethics: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify actions that support ethical culture, prevent misconduct, and encourage transparency and fairness across teams.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'business-ethics-in-practice-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Business Ethics Fundamentals Module from the Business Ethics in Practice Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards Token</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Business Ethics in Practice </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Business Ethics in Practice </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Business Ethics in Practice M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4880/mod_resource/content/1/Business%20Ethics%20Fundamentals%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Business Ethics Fundamentals Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>business ethics</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-what </strong>is workplace integrity</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to maintain your integrity at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to be an ethical employee</li>\r\n<li><strong>Avoid </strong>unethical behavior in the workplace</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4886/mod_resource/content/1/Bussiness%20Ethics%20Fund%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bussiness Ethics Fund Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'business-ethics-in-practice-module-1-business-ethics-fundamentals';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Leadership on Ethics Module from the Business Ethics in Practice Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards Token</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Business Ethics in Practice </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Business Ethics in Practice </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Business Ethics in Practice M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4881/mod_resource/content/1/Leadership%20on%20Ethics%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leadership on Ethics Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>ethical leadership and why its important in the workplace</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability </strong>to create an employee code of conduct</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to develop ethical employees</li>\r\n<li><strong>Make </strong>ethics part of your company culture</li>\r\n<li><strong>Evaluate </strong>employees performance fairly</li>\r\n<li><strong>Make </strong>ethical decisions as a leader</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4887/mod_resource/content/1/Leadership%20on%20Ethics%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leadership on Ethics Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'business-ethics-in-practice-module-2-leadership-on-ethics';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Employee Ethics Module from the Business Ethics in Practice Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>Vow Rewards Token</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Business Ethics in Practice </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Business Ethics in Practice </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Business Ethics in Practice M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4882/mod_resource/content/1/Employee%20Ethics%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Employee Ethics Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>ethical dilemmas and how to resolve them</li>\r\n<li><strong>Overcome </strong>rationalizations when making ethical decisions</li>\r\n<li><strong>Avoid </strong>plagiarism in the workplace</li>\r\n<li><strong>Avoid </strong>motivated ignorance</li>\r\n<li><strong>Enable </strong>reporting of unethical behavior at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Implement </strong>appropriate use of company assets</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4888/mod_resource/content/1/Employee%20Ethics%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Employee Ethics Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'business-ethics-in-practice-module-3-employee-ethics';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Business Ethics in Practice Course</strong> has provided you with essential knowledge and tools to support ethical thinking and responsible behavior in work environments. You explored foundational ethical principles, studied how leaders shape ethical culture, and learned the role employees play in maintaining trust and professionalism. These insights prepare you to evaluate ethical challenges, make thoughtful decisions, and contribute positively to your organization’s integrity and reputation.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on the ethical frameworks, leadership practices, and employee responsibilities discussed throughout each module. Ethical behavior is a continuous commitment that strengthens relationships, enhances organizational performance, and supports long-term success.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to uphold ethical standards, act with integrity, and contribute to a trustworthy and responsible workplace.</span></p>' WHERE slug = 'business-ethics-in-practice-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE INTRODUCTION</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Welcome to the <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture Course</strong>, a practical and empowering learning experience designed to help you understand how healthy workplace cultures are created, strengthened, and sustained. A positive organizational culture is the foundation of employee well-being, motivation, engagement, and long-term organizational success. This course explores how inclusion, respect, effective communication, and cultural competence shape workplace environments where people feel valued, supported, and empowered to contribute their best.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Through relatable examples and real workplace scenarios, you will learn how to interact respectfully, communicate inclusively, and navigate cultural differences in a way that promotes fairness, belonging, and collaboration across teams.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE PURPOSE</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to develop an understanding of how individual behaviors, communication practices, and cultural awareness contribute to building and sustaining a positive organizational culture. Learners will gain the tools to create more inclusive workplaces, foster respect among colleagues, and promote cultural competence across diverse teams.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course equips learners—from students to team leaders and employees—with the knowledge and confidence to participate actively in shaping the culture of their organizations.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE OBJECTIVES</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">1. Understand the foundations of positive organizational culture: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Explain what a positive culture looks like and how it impacts employee morale, performance, and organizational success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">2. Demonstrate inclusion and respect in the workplace: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize inclusive behaviors, demonstrate respect for differences, and foster positive interactions among colleagues.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">3. Use inclusive communication techniques: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Communicate in ways that are clear, respectful, culturally aware, and accessible to people with diverse backgrounds and abilities.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">4. Build cultural competence: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand cultural diversity, recognize its importance, and apply strategies to navigate cultural differences effectively.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 3;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">5. Contribute to a culture of belonging: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Engage in behaviors that support fairness, reduce bias, encourage collaboration, and help all employees feel valued and included.</span></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'improving-business-ethics-amp-culture-course-introduction-purpose-and-objectives';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Business Ethics Fundamentals Module from the Building a Positive Organizational Culture Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4918/mod_resource/content/1/Inclusion%20and%20Respect%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Inclusion and Respect Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to foster psychological safety in the workplace</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability</strong> to create an inclusive remote environment</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>the gender spectrum</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fight </strong>gender bias at work</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4924/mod_resource/content/1/Inclusion%20and%20Respect%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Inclusion and Respect Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'improving-business-ethics-amp-culture-module-1-inclusion-and-respect';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Inclusive Communication Module from the Building a Positive Organizational Culture Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4919/mod_resource/content/1/Inclusive%20Communication-%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Inclusive Communication- Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how</strong> to have inclusive conversations</li>\r\n<li> <strong>Know-how</strong> to handle offensive comments at work</li>\r\n<li>have the <strong>capability</strong> to recover when your impact does not match your intent</li>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>and amplify employee voice</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-when </strong>and how to apologize at work</li>\r\n<li><strong>Create </strong>and use shared agreements</li>\r\n<li><strong>Replace </strong>harmful phrases with inclusive language</li>\r\n<li><strong>Use </strong>gender inclusive language</li>\r\n<li><strong>Use </strong>inclusive language around orientation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Use </strong>racially and ethnically inclusive language</li>\r\n<li><strong>Use </strong>disability inclusive language</li>\r\n<li><strong>Challenge </strong>assumptions for better workplace relationship</li>\r\n<li><strong>Enable </strong>a quick guide to accessible writing</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4925/mod_resource/content/1/Inclusive%20Communication%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Inclusive Communication Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'improving-business-ethics-amp-culture-module-2-inclusive-communication';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr"><strong>Welcome to Culture Competence Module from the Building a Positive Organizational Culture Course</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After completing this module you will receive a <strong>C</strong><strong>ompletion Badge</strong> for social media sharing and <strong>GoalVow (GV) Tokens</strong> that can be used to enrol on more modules.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">This module is <strong>one of three modules</strong> from the <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture </strong>Course and after completing all three modules, you will receive a <strong><a title="Certificate of Completion" href="https://goalvow.com/mod/customcert/view.php?id=1040">Certificate of Completion</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Once you receive your <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture </strong>Course<strong> </strong>Certificate, you can apply to be a GoalVow Academy <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture M</strong><strong>entor</strong> for other Learners and earn more GV Tokens.</p></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4920/mod_resource/content/1/Culture%20Competence%20Module%20Preview.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Culture Competence Module Preview.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4 dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></h4>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>After completing this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Understand </strong>and develop cultural competence</li>\r\n<li>Have the <strong>capability </strong>to present information across cultures</li>\r\n<li><strong>Know-how </strong>to move through the stages of cultural sensitivity</li>\r\n<li><strong>Manage </strong>multicultural teams</li>\r\n<li><strong>Avoid</strong> cultural appropriation</li>\r\n<li><strong>Accommodate </strong>religion, spirituality and beliefs in the workplace</li>\r\n<li><strong>Enable </strong>discussions involving hot-buttons issues</li>\r\n</ul></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/webservice/pluginfile.php/4926/mod_resource/content/1/Culture%20Competence%20Module%20Material.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=00536e412fb8d765b656ee064bf9ca2c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Culture Competence Module Material.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'improving-business-ethics-amp-culture-module-3-culture-competence';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-outline-level: 1;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">COURSE SUMMARY</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The <strong>Building a Positive Organizational Culture Course</strong> has equipped you with essential knowledge and skills to help create workplaces where inclusion, respect, and collaboration thrive. Across the modules, you explored how inclusive behaviors shape team dynamics, how communication influences belonging, and how cultural competence strengthens relationships and organizational performance. You also learned how small, everyday actions can have a powerful impact on workplace culture.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As you prepare for the final assessment, reflect on how you can apply these principles in your daily interactions and contribute meaningfully to positive organizational culture. These skills will help you build stronger relationships, reduce conflict, and create workplace environments where everyone feels valued.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-ZA; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;">Completing this course demonstrates your readiness to support culture-building efforts and actively contribute to creating inclusive, respectful, and high-performing workplaces.</span></p>' WHERE slug = 'improving-business-ethics-amp-culture-course-summary-and-final-exam';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4 style="text-align: center;" data-start="205" data-end="240">Career Management Strategies - Course Preview</h4>\r\n<p data-start="241" data-end="287"><strong data-start="241" data-end="259">Skill Pathway:</strong> Career Development Skills</p>\r\n<p data-start="241" data-end="287" style="text-align: center;"><img class="img-fluid" src="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/pluginfile.php/5071/mod_label/intro/1_Career%20Management%20Strategies%20Course%20Preview%20Thumbnail.png" alt="Career Management Strategies Course Preview Thumbnail" width="751" height="500"></p>\r\n<p data-start="289" data-end="375" style="text-align: center;"><button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/course/view.php?id=395">Watch Course Preview</a></button></p>\r\n<p data-start="289" data-end="375">Build a <strong data-start="665" data-end="708">clear, confident, and strategic roadmap</strong> for long-term professional growth. This course empowers you to take control of your career decisions, develop job-ready skills, and navigate today’s evolving workplace with confidence.</p>\r\n<p data-start="377" data-end="397"><strong data-start="377" data-end="395">Key Highlights</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start="398" data-end="564">\r\n<li data-start="398" data-end="420">\r\n<p data-start="400" data-end="420" style="line-height: 1.5;">🎯 Level: Beginner</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 1.5;" data-start="421" data-end="444">\r\n<p data-start="423" data-end="444">⏱ Duration: 8 Weeks</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 1.5;" data-start="445" data-end="502">\r\n<p data-start="447" data-end="502">🎓 Certificate: GoalVow CPD Certificate of Completion</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 1.5;" data-start="503" data-end="534">\r\n<p data-start="505" data-end="534">⭐ Course Rating: ★★★★☆</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 1.5;" data-start="535" data-end="564">\r\n<p data-start="537" data-end="564">👥 Enrolled Learners: 241+</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">💻 Format: Online, flexible learning</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">💰 Cost: Free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start="566" data-end="625" style="text-align: center;"><strong data-start="569" data-end="592"> <button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/course/view.php?id=274">Enrol for Free</a></button></strong></p>\r\n<h4 data-start="632" data-end="652">Course Overview</h4>\r\n<p data-start="1253" data-end="1409">The <strong data-start="1257" data-end="1289">Career Management Strategies</strong> course is a practical and empowering learning experience designed to help you actively shape your professional journey.</p>\r\n<p data-start="1411" data-end="1427">Whether you are:</p>\r\n<ul data-start="1428" data-end="1542">\r\n<li data-start="1428" data-end="1472">\r\n<p data-start="1430" data-end="1472">entering the workforce for the first time,</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="1473" data-end="1503">\r\n<p data-start="1475" data-end="1503">planning a career change, or</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="1504" data-end="1542">\r\n<p data-start="1506" data-end="1542">seeking growth in your current role,</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start="1544" data-end="1639">this course provides the tools, confidence, and strategies needed to move forward with purpose.</p>\r\n<p data-start="1641" data-end="1756">Through <strong data-start="1649" data-end="1672">expert-led learning</strong>, <strong data-start="1674" data-end="1699">interactive exercises</strong>, and <strong data-start="1705" data-end="1732">real-world applications</strong>, you’ll explore how to:</p>\r\n<ul data-start="1757" data-end="1916">\r\n<li data-start="1757" data-end="1783">\r\n<p data-start="1759" data-end="1783">identify your strengths,</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="1784" data-end="1827">\r\n<p data-start="1786" data-end="1827">build a compelling professional identity,</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="1828" data-end="1876">\r\n<p data-start="1830" data-end="1876">create meaningful workplace relationships, and</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="1877" data-end="1916">\r\n<p data-start="1879" data-end="1916">confidently pursue new opportunities.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start="1918" data-end="2025">By the end of the course, you won’t just understand career management, <strong data-start="1990" data-end="2024">you’ll be ready to take action</strong>.</p>\r\n<h4 data-start="1517" data-end="1537">Course Purpose</h4>\r\n<p data-start="2051" data-end="2224">The purpose of this course is to <strong data-start="2084" data-end="2176">empower learners with practical career-management skills, self-awareness, and confidence</strong> to succeed in modern professional environments.</p>\r\n<p data-start="2226" data-end="2258">This course enables learners to:</p>\r\n<ul data-start="2259" data-end="2425">\r\n<li data-start="2259" data-end="2300">\r\n<p data-start="2261" data-end="2300">take ownership of their career journey,</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2301" data-end="2334">\r\n<p data-start="2303" data-end="2334">make informed career decisions,</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2335" data-end="2371">\r\n<p data-start="2337" data-end="2371">adapt to workplace challenges, and</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2372" data-end="2425">\r\n<p data-start="2374" data-end="2425">pursue meaningful, sustainable professional growth.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="1969" data-end="1994">Learning Objectives</h4>\r\n<p data-start="1996" data-end="2043">By the end of this course, you will be able to:</p>\r\n<ul data-start="2045" data-end="2410">\r\n<li data-start="2045" data-end="2108">\r\n<p data-start="2047" data-end="2108">Clarify and shape your career direction and long-term goals</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2109" data-end="2168">\r\n<p data-start="2111" data-end="2168">Identify, assess, and develop your strengths and skills</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2169" data-end="2224">\r\n<p data-start="2171" data-end="2224">Apply effective job search and interview strategies</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2225" data-end="2287">\r\n<p data-start="2227" data-end="2287">Transition confidently into professional work environments</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2288" data-end="2344">\r\n<p data-start="2290" data-end="2344">Build strong professional networks and relationships</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2345" data-end="2410">\r\n<p data-start="2347" data-end="2410">Demonstrate professionalism and adaptability in the workplace</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;" data-start="2417" data-end="2449">Course Structure &amp; Modules</h3>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/pluginfile.php/5071/mod_label/intro/image.png" width="580" height="481"></p>\r\n<h4 data-start="2451" data-end="2498">Course Introduction, Purpose &amp; Objectives</h4>\r\n<p data-start="2499" data-end="2606">Get oriented with the course structure and understand how to navigate your learning journey successfully.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="2607" data-end="2734">\r\n<li data-start="2607" data-end="2650">\r\n<p data-start="2609" data-end="2650">Understand how the course is structured</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2651" data-end="2701">\r\n<p data-start="2653" data-end="2701">Learn how to maximize your learning experience</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2702" data-end="2734">\r\n<p data-start="2704" data-end="2734">Set expectations for success</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="2741" data-end="2787">Module 1: Driving Your Career to Success</h4>\r\n<p data-start="2788" data-end="2872">Learn how to take ownership of your career and define your professional direction.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="2873" data-end="2991">\r\n<li data-start="2873" data-end="2917">\r\n<p data-start="2875" data-end="2917">Understand what career development means</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2918" data-end="2944">\r\n<p data-start="2920" data-end="2944">Set clear career goals</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="2945" data-end="2991">\r\n<p data-start="2947" data-end="2991">Take responsibility for your career growth</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="2998" data-end="3049">Module 2: Assessing Your Strengths and Skills</h4>\r\n<p data-start="3050" data-end="3120">Identify what makes you valuable and how to build on your strengths.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="3121" data-end="3249">\r\n<li data-start="3121" data-end="3161">\r\n<p data-start="3123" data-end="3161">Discover your key skills and talents</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="3162" data-end="3196">\r\n<p data-start="3164" data-end="3196">Identify areas for improvement</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="3197" data-end="3249">\r\n<p data-start="3199" data-end="3249">Learn how to position your strengths effectively</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="3256" data-end="3289">Module 3: Finding a New Job</h4>\r\n<p data-start="3290" data-end="3361">Develop strategies to search for and secure new career opportunities.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="3362" data-end="3464">\r\n<li data-start="3362" data-end="3395">\r\n<p data-start="3364" data-end="3395">Explore job search techniques</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="3396" data-end="3427">\r\n<p data-start="3398" data-end="3427">Prepare strong applications</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="3428" data-end="3464">\r\n<p data-start="3430" data-end="3464">Understand employer expectations</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="3471" data-end="3503">Module 4: New Professional</h4>\r\n<p data-start="3504" data-end="3565">Transition confidently into professional work environments.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="3566" data-end="3664">\r\n<li data-start="3566" data-end="3598">\r\n<p data-start="3568" data-end="3598">Understand workplace culture</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="3599" data-end="3631">\r\n<p data-start="3601" data-end="3631">Develop professional mindset</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="3632" data-end="3664">\r\n<p data-start="3634" data-end="3664">Learn workplace expectations</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="3671" data-end="3697">Module 5: Networking</h4>\r\n<p data-start="3698" data-end="3764">Build and leverage professional relationships for career growth.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="3765" data-end="3899">\r\n<li data-start="3765" data-end="3803">\r\n<p data-start="3767" data-end="3803">Understand the power of networking</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="3804" data-end="3849">\r\n<p data-start="3806" data-end="3849">Build meaningful professional connections</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="3850" data-end="3899">\r\n<p data-start="3852" data-end="3899">Maintain long-term professional relationships</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="3906" data-end="3948">Module 6: Mentoring in the Workplace</h4>\r\n<p data-start="3949" data-end="4007">Learn how mentoring can support your career development.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="4008" data-end="4118">\r\n<li data-start="4008" data-end="4042">\r\n<p data-start="4010" data-end="4042">Understand the role of mentors</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="4043" data-end="4073">\r\n<p data-start="4045" data-end="4073">Learn how to find a mentor</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="4074" data-end="4118">\r\n<p data-start="4076" data-end="4118">Build productive mentoring relationships</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="4125" data-end="4163">Module 7: Professional Etiquette</h4>\r\n<p data-start="4164" data-end="4224">Demonstrate professionalism in communication and behavior.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="4225" data-end="4325">\r\n<li data-start="4225" data-end="4254">\r\n<p data-start="4227" data-end="4254">Apply workplace etiquette</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="4255" data-end="4285">\r\n<p data-start="4257" data-end="4285">Communicate professionally</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="4286" data-end="4325">\r\n<p data-start="4288" data-end="4325">Build a positive professional image</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="4332" data-end="4369">Module 8: Working Relationships</h4>\r\n<p data-start="4370" data-end="4426">Develop strong collaboration and communication skills.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="4427" data-end="4543">\r\n<li data-start="4427" data-end="4469">\r\n<p data-start="4429" data-end="4469">Build positive workplace relationships</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="4470" data-end="4505">\r\n<p data-start="4472" data-end="4505">Resolve conflict professionally</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="4506" data-end="4543">\r\n<p data-start="4508" data-end="4543">Work effectively in diverse teams</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="4550" data-end="4587">Module 9: Overcoming Challenges</h4>\r\n<p data-start="4588" data-end="4654">Build resilience and adaptability to manage workplace obstacles.</p>\r\n<ul data-start="4655" data-end="4759">\r\n<li data-start="4655" data-end="4693">\r\n<p data-start="4657" data-end="4693">Develop problem-solving strategies</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="4694" data-end="4724">\r\n<p data-start="4696" data-end="4724">Build emotional resilience</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="4725" data-end="4759">\r\n<p data-start="4727" data-end="4759">Adapt to change and challenges</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="4766" data-end="4801">Course Summary &amp; Final Exam</h4>\r\n<p data-start="4802" data-end="4917">Review key concepts and demonstrate your understanding through a final assessment to confirm your career readiness.</p>\r\n<h4 data-start="4924" data-end="4957">Certificate of Completion</h4>\r\n<p data-start="4958" data-end="5086">Upon successful completion, learners will receive a <strong data-start="4271" data-end="4312">GoalVow CPD Certificate of Completion</strong>, validating their skills and commitment to professional development</p>\r\n<h4 data-start="5093" data-end="5115">What You’ll Gain</h4>\r\n<ul data-start="5117" data-end="5334">\r\n<li data-start="5117" data-end="5166">\r\n<p data-start="5119" data-end="5166">Practical, job-ready career management skills</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="5167" data-end="5228">\r\n<p data-start="5169" data-end="5228">Confidence to apply learning in real workplace situations</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="5229" data-end="5280">\r\n<p data-start="5231" data-end="5280">Exposure to modern career development practices</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="5281" data-end="5334">\r\n<p data-start="5283" data-end="5334">A recognized certificate to support career growth</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 data-start="5341" data-end="5369">Who This Course Is For</h4>\r\n<ul data-start="5371" data-end="5557">\r\n<li data-start="5371" data-end="5425">\r\n<p data-start="5373" data-end="5425">Students and school leavers entering the workforce</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="5426" data-end="5461">\r\n<p data-start="5428" data-end="5461">Job seekers and career changers</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="5462" data-end="5492">\r\n<p data-start="5464" data-end="5492">Early-career professionals</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="5493" data-end="5557">\r\n<p data-start="5495" data-end="5557">Anyone looking to grow and manage their career strategically</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;" data-start="5564" data-end="5590">Ready to Get Started.</h4>\r\n<p data-start="5592" data-end="5633" style="text-align: center;">This course is <strong data-start="5607" data-end="5630">free and self-paced</strong>.</p>\r\n<p data-start="5635" data-end="5691" style="text-align: center;"><strong data-start="5638" data-end="5652"> <button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/course/view.php?id=274">Enroll Now</a></button>                                                           <button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/course/index.php">Explore more Upskilling courses</a></button></strong></p></div>' WHERE slug = 'career-management-strategies-course-preview';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 24.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Human Resource Essentials - Course Preview</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Skill Pathway: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Human Resource Skills</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><img class="img-fluid" src="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/pluginfile.php/5095/mod_label/intro/2_Human%20Resource%20Essentials%20Course%20Preview%20Thumbnail.png" alt="Human Resource Essentials Course Preview Thumbnail" width="750" height="500"></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"><button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/course/view.php?id=396">Watch Course Preview</a></button> </span></p>\r\n<p data-start="644" data-end="742" style="line-height: 2;">Master the fundamentals of modern HR to recruit, develop &amp; retain performing talent.</p>\r\n<p data-start="377" data-end="397" style="line-height: 2;"><strong data-start="377" data-end="395">Key Highlights</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start="398" data-end="564">\r\n<li data-start="398" data-end="420">\r\n<p data-start="400" data-end="420">🎯 Level: Beginner</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="421" data-end="444">\r\n<p data-start="423" data-end="444">⏱ Duration: 9 Weeks (self-paced)</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="445" data-end="502">\r\n<p data-start="447" data-end="502">🎓 Certificate: GoalVow CPD Certificate of Completion</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="503" data-end="534">\r\n<p data-start="505" data-end="534">⭐Course Rating: 4.8/5</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start="535" data-end="564">\r\n<p data-start="537" data-end="564">👥 Enrolled Learners: 324+</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;" data-start="535" data-end="564">💻 Format: Online, flexible learning</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">💰 Cost: Free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start="566" data-end="625" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong data-start="569" data-end="592"> <button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/enrol/index.php?id=275">Enroll for Free</a></button></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Overview</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The Human Resource Essentials course is a comprehensive, practical introduction to the core functions of Human Resource Management in modern organizations. This course equips learners with the essential knowledge and skills required to support people, build strong workplace cultures, and contribute to organizational success.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Throughout this course, you will explore how HR supports recruitment, employee development, workplace diversity, performance management, well-being, and compliance. You will gain insight into real-world HR practices and learn how HR professionals help organizations attract, engage, and retain talent.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Whether you are new to HR, transitioning into an HR role, or looking to strengthen your understanding of people management, this course provides a solid foundation for building confidence and competence in Human Resources.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Purpose</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of the Human Resource Essentials course is to prepare learners with the practical HR knowledge and workplace awareness needed to support employees and organizations effectively. This course helps learners understand how HR contributes to recruitment, performance, workplace culture, and compliance — enabling them to add value in any people-focused role.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Learning Objectives</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, learners will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand the core functions and responsibilities of Human Resources</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply HR best practices in recruitment and interviewing</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Promote diversity, inclusion, and fair workplace practices</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support employee well-being and performance management</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify and manage unconscious bias in the workplace</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply HR policies and procedures ethically and professionally</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Structure &amp; Modules</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"><img src="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/pluginfile.php/5095/mod_label/i