mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize how HR supports business success</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Module 2: Diversity, Inclusion and Belonging</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Create fair, inclusive, and respectful workplaces.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">You will learn to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand diversity and inclusion principles</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Promote belonging in the workplace</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support fair and equitable treatment</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Module 3: Interviewing</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Develop effective interviewing and candidate selection skills.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">You will learn to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Prepare for structured interviews</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Ask effective interview questions</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support fair hiring decisions</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Module 4: Unconscious Bias</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize and manage bias in HR and workplace decisions.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">You will learn to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify common forms of unconscious bias</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand how bias affects decisions</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply strategies to reduce bias</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Module 5: Talent Management</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support employee growth and performance.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">You will learn to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand talent development strategies</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support performance management</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Promote employee engagement</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style