 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">You will learn to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand harassment and discrimination policies</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize inappropriate workplace behavior</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support safe and compliant work environments</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Module 8: Retirement Planning</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support employees through later career stages.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">You will learn to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand retirement planning basics</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support employee transition planning</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Recognize HR’s role in retirement processes</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Summary &amp; Final Exam</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Review key Human Resource concepts and demonstrate your understanding through a final assessment to confirm your learning and practical application.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Certificate of Completion</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Upon successful completion, you will earn a <strong>GoalVow CPD Certificate of Completion</strong>, validating your HR knowledge and supporting your professional growth.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">What You’ll Gain in This Course</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; fo