elp you take control of your time, increase productivity, and focus on what truly matters. In today’s fast-paced world, managing competing demands and staying organized is essential for both personal and professional success.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course equips you with practical tools and techniques to plan effectively, set meaningful goals, prioritize tasks, and maintain focus. You will learn how to reduce time-wasting habits, manage distractions, and create systems that support consistent progress.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be able to work smarter, stay organized, and achieve more with less stress.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Purpose</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of the Time Management &amp; Prioritization course is to empower learners with structured strategies to manage their time effectively, prioritize important tasks, and maintain focus in busy environments. This course supports learners in developing habits that improve efficiency, reduce overwhelm, and enhance long-term productivity.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times 