UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 24.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Cybersecurity Basics</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Skills Pathway:</span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"> Information Technology Skills</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><img class="img-fluid" src="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/pluginfile.php/5112/mod_label/intro/12_Cybersecurity%20Basics%20Course%20Preview%20Thumbnail2.png" alt="Cybersecurity Basics Course Preview Thumbnail" width="750" height="500"></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"><button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/course/view.php?id=406">Watch Course Preview</a></button></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Learn how to protect your data, devices, and organization from online threats.</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">🎯 <strong>Level:</strong> Beginner</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">⏱ <strong>Duration:</strong> 3 weeks</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">🎓 <strong>Certificate:</strong> GoalVow CPD Certificate of Completion</span></li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">Course Rating: ⭐⭐⭐⭐</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">👥 <strong>Enrolled Learners:</strong> 94+</span></li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">💻 Format: Online, flexible learning</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">💰 Cost: Free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong data-start="569" data-end="592"> <button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/enrol/index.php?id=288">Enrol for Free</a></button></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Overview</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The Cybersecurity Basics course is designed to give you a practical foundation in protecting yourself and your organization from today’s most common online threats.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">As digital tools become essential in everyday work, cyber risks such as phishing, data breaches, and identity theft are increasing. This course helps you understand these risks and apply simple, effective security practices to protect sensitive information.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By completing this course, you will be equipped with essential cybersecurity awareness and practical skills to reduce risk and improve digital safety at work and at home.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Purpose</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of the Cybersecurity Basics course is to empower learners with fundamental knowledge and practical strategies to protect data, devices, and digital identities. This course builds awareness of cyber threats and equips individuals with everyday security practices that reduce vulnerability and strengthen organizational security.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Learning Objectives</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By completing this cours