; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Learning Objectives</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By completing this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand the fundamentals of effective leadership</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Identify and apply different leadership styles</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Develop emotional intelligence for leadership success</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Build trust and integrity as a leader</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Communicate vision and direction clearly</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Motivate and inspire team members</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New