UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 24.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Leading Through Change</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Skill Pathway: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Change Management Skills</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"><img class="img-fluid" src="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/pluginfile.php/5119/mod_label/intro/15_Leading%20Through%20Change%20Course%20Preview%20Thumbnail.png" alt="Leading Through Change Course Preview Thumbnail" width="750" height="500"></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;"><button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/course/view.php?id=409">Watch Course Preview</a></button></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Learn to lead organizational change with resilience and clear communication.</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">🎯 <strong>Level:</strong> Beginner</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">⏱ <strong>Duration:</strong> 6 weeks</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">🎓 <strong>Certificate:</strong> GoalVow CPD Certificate of Completion</span></li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">Course Rating: ⭐⭐⭐⭐</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">👥 <strong>Enrolled Learners:</strong> 67+</span></li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">💻 Format: Online, flexible learning</li>\r\n<li style="line-height: 2;">💰 Cost: Free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong data-start="569" data-end="592"><button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/enrol/index.php?id=389">Enrol for Free</a></button></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Overview</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The Leading Through Change course equips you with the essential skills to guide individuals and teams through organizational change with confidence and clarity.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">In today’s fast-changing business environment, leaders must be able to manage uncertainty, communicate effectively, and support people through transitions. This course provides practical frameworks and leadership strategies to help you lead change initiatives, reduce resistance, and build resilience within your organization.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By the end of this course, you will be prepared to lead change efforts that drive positive outcomes while maintaining team engagement and trust.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Purpose</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of the Leading Through Change course is to empower learners with practical change management knowledge and leadership tools to successfully guide teams and organizations through periods of transition, disruption, and transformation.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Learning Objectives</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By completing this course, you will be able to:</span></p>\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Understand the fundamentals of change management</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Apply change management models in real-world scenarios</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Lead structured change processes</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Communicate change effectively to stakeholders</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Support teams through uncertainty and resistance</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Lead confidently during times of crisis</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Build resilience and adaptability in yourself and others</span></li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal