its, and practical skills to support their mental, emotional, and physical well-being in today’s demanding work environments.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course focuses on positive psychology, healthy lifestyle habits, emotional awareness, and workplace mental health — empowering learners to build resilience, improve focus, and maintain a healthy work-life balance.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">By completing this course, you will gain practical strategies to manage stress, support your mental health, and contribute to a healthier, more positive workplace culture.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Course Purpose</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">The purpose of this course is to equip learners with practical tools and knowledge to improve mental, emotional, and physical wellness, enabling greater resilience, productivity, and overall life balance in both professional and personal environments.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">Learning Objectives</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'T