nt-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-fareast-language: EN-ZA;">This course is <strong>free and self-paced</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2; text-align: center;"><strong data-start="5638" data-end="5652"><button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/enrol/index.php?id=394">Enroll Now</a></button>                                                           <button class="btn btn-primary lambdacep" type="button"><a href="https://goalvow.com/upskilling/course/index.php">Explore more Upskilling courses</a></button></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 2;"> </p></div>' WHERE slug = 'improving-business-ethics-amp-culture-course-preview';

