0Relationship.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Employee Employer Relationship.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1313/mod_resource/content/1/Employee%20Employer%20Relationship.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Employee Employer Relationship.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'commercial-ablution-cleaner-theory-knowledge-module-3-cleaning-ablution-facilities';
