f</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 3 (KT03) | Types, Functions of Consumables</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1005/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%203.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 3.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 4 (KT04) | Categories of Chemicals</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1029/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic4.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic4.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 5 (KT05) | Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1065/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%205.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 5.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'commercial-floor-cleaner-knowledge-module-2-commercial-cleaning-equipment-chemicals-and-consumables';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h4> </h4>\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 1 (KT01) | Basics of floor types</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1339/mod_resource/content/1/1_KM%201_Intro%20to%20World%20of%20Work_Topic%201.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1_KM 1_Intro to World of Work_Topic 1.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1348/mod_resource/content/1/1_KM%201_Intro%20to%20World%20of%20Work_Topic%201.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1_KM 1_Intro to World of Work_Topic 1.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4> </h4>\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 2 (KT02) | Cleaning methodologies of floor types</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1344/mod_resource/content/1/1_KM%201_Intro%20to%20World%20of%20Work_Topic%201.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1_KM 1_Intro to World of Work_Topic 1.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1350/mod_resource/content/1/1_KM%201_Intro%20to%20World%20of%20Work_Topic%201.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1_KM 1_Intro to World of Work_Topic 1.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4> </h4>\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 3 (KT03) | Maintenance of floors</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1353/mod_resource/content/1/1_KM%201_Intro%20to%20World%20of%20Work_Topic%201.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1_KM 1_Intro to World of Work_Topic 1.pdf</a></p>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1357/mod_resource/content/1/1_KM%201_Intro%20to%20World%20of%20Work_Topic%201.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1_KM 1_Intro to World of Work_Topic 1.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'commercial-floor-cleaner-knowledge-module-3-basics-of-cleaning-commercial-floor-surface';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h5><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Purpose</strong></span></h5>\r\n<p>The purpose of this course is to prepare the learner to function as a Commercial Kitchenette Cleaner in the workplace.</p>\r\n<p>A Commercial Kitchenette Cleaner, cleans and maintains a commercial kitchenette which is a workplace kitchen.</p>\r\n<p>In addition, learner attributes(including communication) will be integrated in the learning process.</p>\r\n<p>Learners will have to prove competence of the above knowledge, skills, attitudes, responsibilities, and tasks imbedded in the exit level outcomes of this course.</p>\r\n<h5><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></span></h5>\r\n<p>After completing this course, a learner will be able to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Prepare equipment and tools, chemical and consumables to clean the kitchenette to specifications.</li>\r\n<li>Complete cleaning of the kitchenette to expected standard using cleaning principles and methods.</li>\r\n</ul></div>' WHERE slug = 'commercial-all-rounder-cleaner-purpose-and-learning-outcome';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h5><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Course Entry Requirements</span></h5>\r\n<p>The minimum entry requirement for this course is:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Open Access, meaning anyone can enrol in this course.</li>\r\n</ul></div>' WHERE slug = 'commercial-all-rounder-cleaner-entry-requirements';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><p></p>\r\n<div class="shadow info-box bg-info-light">\r\n<div class="icon-circle info"><span class="sr-only">info</span></div>\r\n<div class="info-body">\r\n<h5>Knowledge Module 1 (KM-01):</h5>\r\n<p class="m-0">The main focus of knowledge module 1 is to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="m-0">Build an understanding of the world of work.</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">Enable the learner to demonstrate an understanding of various work related requirements like:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-01-KT01: Employment Contract (20%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-01-KT02: Organizational work (20%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-01-KT03: Employer-Employee relationships (15%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-01-KT04: Concepts related to the performance of work (15%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-01-KT05: Ethics at work (10%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-01-KT06: Current trends influencing work (10%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-01-KT07: Basic Communication Skills (10%)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><em>Time duration to complete this module, is at least 7 days.</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 1 (KT01) | Employment Contract</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1093/mod_resource/content/1/1_KM%201_Intro%20to%20World%20of%20Work_Topic%201.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1_KM 1_Intro to World of Work_Topic 1.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 2 (KT02) | Organizational Work</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1114/mod_resource/content/1/1_KM%201_Intro%20to%20World%20of%20Work_Topic%202.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1_KM 1_Intro to World of Work_Topic 2.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 3 (KT03) | Employer-Employee Relationships</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1140/mod_resource/content/1/Employee%20Employer%20Relationship.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Employee Employer Relationship.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 4 (KT04) | Concepts related to the performance of work</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1162/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%204.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 4.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4>Topic 5 (KT05) | Ethics at Work</h4>\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1189/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%205.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 5.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><p></p>\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 6 (KT06) | Current trends influencing work </h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1221/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%206.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 6.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><p></p>\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 7 (KT07) | Basic Communication Skills</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1248/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%207.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 7.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><p></p>\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Survey | Rate this Module</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>' WHERE slug = 'commercial-all-rounder-cleaner-theory-knowledge-module-1-introduction-to-the-world-of-work';
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="no-overflow"><h5> </h5>\r\n<div class="info-box bg-info-light">\r\n<div class="icon-circle info"><span class="sr-only">info</span></div>\r\n<div class="info-body">\r\n<h5>Knowledge Module 2 (KM-02):</h5>\r\n<p class="m-0">The main focus of knowledge module 2 is to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="m-0">Build an understanding of the commercial cleaning equipment and chemicals.</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">The knowledge acquired will enable the learner to demonstrate an understanding of:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-02-KT01: Types and functions of Cleaning Equipment (20%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-02-KT02: Handling and caring for equipment (20%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-02-KT03: Types, functions of consumables (20%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-02-KT04: Categories of Chemicals (20%)</li>\r\n<li class="m-0">KM-02-KT05: Personal Protective Equipment (PPE) (20%)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><em>Time duration to complete this module, is at least 6.25 days</em></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><em>.</em></p></div>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><h4> </h4>\r\n<div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 1 (KT01) | Types and Functions of Cleaning Equipment</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/951/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20Topic%201.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material Topic 1.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 2 (KT02) | Handling and Caring for Equipment</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/980/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%202.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 2.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 3 (KT03) | Types, Functions of Consumables</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1006/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%203.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 3.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 4 (KT04) | Categories of Chemicals</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1030/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic4.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic4.pdf</a></p>\n\n<div class="no-overflow"><div class="section-heading">\r\n<h4>Topic 5 (KT05) | Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)</h4>\r\n<div class="divider line-01"> </div>\r\n</div></div>\n\n<p>📎 <a href="https://goalvow.com/skills-training/webservice/pluginfile.php/1066/mod_resource/content/1/Reading%20Material%20for%20Topic%205.pdf?forcedownload=1?token=6b5f00ce3889922a6eb1df2b4a8c45aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reading Material for Topic 5.pdf</a></p>' WHERE slug = 'commercial-all-rounder-cleaner-theory-knowledge-module-2-commercial-cleaning-equipment-chemicals-and-consumable';
